00:00:49.468 --> 00:00:52.771 position:16% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] You young ones
are persistent, aren't you?

00:00:52.804 --> 00:00:53.872 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ah, very well.

00:00:53.905 --> 00:00:57.542 position:10% line:83% align:start
If you must know the story,
I'm the one to tell it.

00:00:57.576 --> 00:01:00.745 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Gather near and
pay close attention, everyone.

00:01:00.779 --> 00:01:03.047 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
A long time ago.

00:01:03.080 --> 00:01:06.183 position:16% line:83% align:start
Hm, actually, it wasn't
long ago at all.

00:01:06.217 --> 00:01:08.018 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why do stories
always start that way?

00:01:08.052 --> 00:01:11.655 position:7% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Anyhow, the story
begins right here in Jutengai,

00:01:11.689 --> 00:01:13.591 position:27% line:83% align:start
a thriving land
that is home to about

00:01:13.624 --> 00:01:15.359 position:10% line:89% align:start
one hundred thousand Beasts.

00:01:15.392 --> 00:01:18.529 position:21% line:83% align:start
The lord of Jutengai
had ruled for many years,

00:01:18.562 --> 00:01:20.731 position:5% line:83% align:start
but then, one day, he announced
that he was going to

00:01:20.764 --> 00:01:25.502 position:21% line:83% align:start
retire from his post
and reincarnate as a god.

00:01:25.535 --> 00:01:27.570 position:19% line:83% align:start
He needed some time to
decide what sort of god

00:01:27.604 --> 00:01:29.339 position:7% line:89% align:start
he wished to become, however.

00:01:29.372 --> 00:01:31.808 position:10% line:83% align:start
Once he reached a decision,
he would determine which Beast

00:01:31.841 --> 00:01:34.043 position:21% line:83% align:start
was worthy to become
the lord in his place.

00:01:34.077 --> 00:01:36.646 position:19% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] His successor
had to be fair, honorable,

00:01:36.679 --> 00:01:38.781 position:16% line:89% align:start
and, of course, strong.

00:01:38.815 --> 00:01:42.485 position:16% line:83% align:start
The first candidate was
a Beast named Iozen.

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:47.389 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Iozen was
fearless and valiant.

00:01:47.422 --> 00:01:49.792 position:10% line:83% align:start
Many apprentices had sought
him out for his fighting prowess

00:01:49.826 --> 00:01:50.760 position:19% line:89% align:start
and teaching ability.

00:01:50.793 --> 00:01:53.529 position:19% line:83% align:start
He was also the proud
father of two sons,

00:01:53.562 --> 00:01:56.431 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ichirohiko and Jiromaru.

00:01:57.799 --> 00:02:00.736 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Everyone was certain
he would be chosen.

00:02:00.769 --> 00:02:03.405 position:19% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] However,
there was another candidate.

00:02:03.438 --> 00:02:05.474 position:21% line:83% align:start
The Beast who would
challenge Iozen.

00:02:05.507 --> 00:02:09.310 position:16% line:89% align:start
His name was Kumatetsu.

00:02:09.343 --> 00:02:12.213 position:16% line:83% align:start
He was tall and shaggy,
with the appearance of a bear.

00:02:12.246 --> 00:02:14.282 position:16% line:83% align:start
But he had the tireless
energy of a monkey,

00:02:14.315 --> 00:02:15.817 position:27% line:83% align:start
dashing back and
forth as he fought,

00:02:15.851 --> 00:02:17.718 position:7% line:89% align:start
swinging his scabbarded sword.

00:02:17.752 --> 00:02:20.821 position:24% line:83% align:start
He and Iozen were
said to be equals.

00:02:22.490 --> 00:02:24.191 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
In terms of strength, anyway.

00:02:24.225 --> 00:02:27.695 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Kumatetsu's character
was a different story.

00:02:27.728 --> 00:02:31.097 position:7% line:83% align:start
He was rough around the edges,
a bit crude, and often selfish.

00:02:31.131 --> 00:02:33.333 position:27% line:83% align:start
He did not have
a single apprentice.

00:02:33.366 --> 00:02:35.235 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Yes, strong
fighter though he was,

00:02:35.268 --> 00:02:38.739 position:19% line:83% align:start
he had no apprentice.
Nor did he have any sons.

00:03:16.909 --> 00:03:17.876 position:30% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN A]
Come here.

00:03:17.910 --> 00:03:19.511 position:27% line:83% align:start
[RUNAWAY GIRL A]
Leave me alone. Don't touch me.

00:03:19.545 --> 00:03:20.512 position:30% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN A]
You're still minors.

00:03:20.546 --> 00:03:21.346 position:27% line:83% align:start
[RUNAWAY GIRL B]
No, we aren't.

00:03:21.379 --> 00:03:22.481 position:30% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN A]
Run away from home?

00:03:22.514 --> 00:03:24.683 position:19% line:83% align:start
[RUNAWAY GIRL B] Geez,
we're just out for the night.

00:03:36.561 --> 00:03:41.566 position:30% line:89% align:start
[REN panting]

00:03:51.241 --> 00:03:55.512 position:30% line:89% align:start
[REN panting]

00:04:04.287 --> 00:04:05.622 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaks]

00:04:08.224 --> 00:04:11.695 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're so tiny. What are you?
A baby mouse, maybe?

00:04:11.728 --> 00:04:13.429 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hold on a sec.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:18.501 position:38% line:89% align:start
Take it.

00:04:18.534 --> 00:04:19.435 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaks]

00:04:19.468 --> 00:04:20.803 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Go on.

00:04:22.805 --> 00:04:25.574 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaks]

00:04:29.945 --> 00:04:31.747 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't think this is
where you belong.

00:04:31.781 --> 00:04:33.281 position:10% line:89% align:start
Did you run away from home?

00:04:33.314 --> 00:04:35.451 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaks]

00:04:35.484 --> 00:04:39.320 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's what I did.
I'm all alone, just like you.

00:04:46.728 --> 00:04:48.363 position:7% line:89% align:start
[MOVERS chatter indistinctly]

00:04:48.396 --> 00:04:50.832 position:35% line:83% align:start
[MOVER B]
That's it for this room.

00:04:50.865 --> 00:04:53.334 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Dad, I don't understand...

00:04:53.368 --> 00:04:54.836 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where are you?

00:04:54.869 --> 00:04:56.805 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why won't you just
come and get me?

00:04:56.838 --> 00:04:59.273 position:24% line:83% align:start
I don't want to go
with these people.

00:04:59.306 --> 00:05:02.677 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE A]
Ren, come on now. Let's go.

00:05:02.711 --> 00:05:05.412 position:10% line:83% align:start
[MOVER C] I'm sorry, but...
what should we do with this?

00:05:05.446 --> 00:05:07.448 position:19% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE RELATIVE] Oh.
We'll take that with us, thanks.

00:05:07.481 --> 00:05:08.950 position:13% line:83% align:start
--[MOVER A, MOVER B grunt]
--[MOVER C] Sure.

00:05:08.983 --> 00:05:10.517 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[MOVER A] Careful!
--[MOVER B] Got it.

00:05:11.552 --> 00:05:12.987 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE A]
I know you miss your mother.

00:05:13.021 --> 00:05:14.621 position:13% line:89% align:start
It was a tragic accident.

00:05:14.655 --> 00:05:16.290 position:24% line:83% align:start
But with her gone,
it's only right

00:05:16.323 --> 00:05:17.825 position:7% line:89% align:start
for her family to take you in.

00:05:17.858 --> 00:05:19.793 position:5% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE B] Things will be
different than you're used to,

00:05:19.827 --> 00:05:21.495 position:7% line:89% align:start
but you'll adjust, you'll see.

00:05:21.528 --> 00:05:22.963 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE RELATIVE A]
We know this is hard for you,

00:05:22.996 --> 00:05:24.330 position:10% line:89% align:start
but you're a big boy, right?

00:05:24.363 --> 00:05:25.666 position:13% line:89% align:start
Just give it a little time

00:05:25.699 --> 00:05:28.202 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I'm sure you'll
be happy with us.

00:05:29.569 --> 00:05:31.337 position:16% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE A] Well?
Are you listening to us?

00:05:31.370 --> 00:05:32.705 position:30% line:89% align:start
Say something.

00:05:37.978 --> 00:05:40.012 position:27% line:83% align:start
Where's my dad?
I should be with him.

00:05:40.046 --> 00:05:41.748 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE A]
No. Forget about him.

00:05:41.781 --> 00:05:44.283 position:33% line:83% align:start
He's my dad.
I can't just forget him.

00:05:44.317 --> 00:05:45.952 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE RELATIVE A]
Your mother obviously wanted to.

00:05:45.985 --> 00:05:47.587 position:24% line:89% align:start
She divorced him.

00:05:47.620 --> 00:05:49.889 position:7% line:83% align:start
We're your closest family now,
remember that.

00:05:49.922 --> 00:05:52.625 position:21% line:83% align:start
You belong with us,
not your father.

00:05:52.658 --> 00:05:55.660 position:24% line:83% align:start
[REN] Fine, then.
I'll go live by myself.

00:05:55.694 --> 00:05:56.963 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE B]
Oh, you're just a child.

00:05:56.996 --> 00:05:59.531 position:10% line:89% align:start
You can't live by yourself.

00:05:59.564 --> 00:06:01.033 position:10% line:89% align:start
I don't need anybody's help!

00:06:01.067 --> 00:06:03.568 position:33% line:83% align:start
Just watch.
I'll get strong and show you!

00:06:03.602 --> 00:06:05.637 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE A]
Stop this nonsense!

00:06:05.670 --> 00:06:06.705 position:13% line:89% align:start
You may be a kid, but I--

00:06:06.738 --> 00:06:09.407 position:27% line:83% align:start
I hate you all!
You guys, my dad,

00:06:09.441 --> 00:06:11.443 position:16% line:89% align:start
everything and everyone!

00:06:11.476 --> 00:06:12.244 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE A]
Ren!

00:06:12.276 --> 00:06:13.377 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE RELATIVE B]
Ren! Come back!

00:06:13.410 --> 00:06:15.412 position:27% line:89% align:start
[car horn honks]

00:06:23.487 --> 00:06:25.523 position:24% line:89% align:start
I hate everybody.

00:06:29.727 --> 00:06:31.695 position:24% line:89% align:start
I hate everybody.

00:06:31.729 --> 00:06:36.033 position:13% line:83% align:start
I hate them. I hate them.
I hate them all.

00:06:36.066 --> 00:06:37.935 position:24% line:89% align:start
I hate everybody!

00:06:37.968 --> 00:06:39.469 position:10% line:89% align:start
[PEOPLE gasping, murmuring]

00:06:39.503 --> 00:06:40.838 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:54.417 --> 00:06:56.386 position:33% line:89% align:start
I hate them.

00:06:56.419 --> 00:07:00.924 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hate... them... Hate them.

00:07:16.672 --> 00:07:18.141 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Hey, Chico.

00:07:18.174 --> 00:07:20.742 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm okay. Thanks for checking.

00:07:20.776 --> 00:07:24.713 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

00:07:27.149 --> 00:07:29.551 position:13% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE] So what if
I don't have any apprentices.

00:07:29.585 --> 00:07:31.887 position:13% line:83% align:start
I just have to be stronger
than Iozen, right?

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:34.422 position:21% line:83% align:start
All the rest is just
for show, anyway.

00:07:34.455 --> 00:07:36.959 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] The lord sets high
standards, you know that.

00:07:36.992 --> 00:07:39.894 position:16% line:83% align:start
You had one apprentice.
How long did he last?

00:07:39.927 --> 00:07:41.963 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
A month. A week?

00:07:41.996 --> 00:07:43.064 position:35% line:89% align:start
No, a day.

00:07:43.098 --> 00:07:44.765 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Not even a whole day!
Just the morning.

00:07:44.799 --> 00:07:46.767 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
Yeah, well, he was a crybaby.

00:07:46.801 --> 00:07:48.970 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Beggars can't be choosers.

00:07:49.003 --> 00:07:50.771 position:13% line:89% align:start
I know! While we're here,

00:07:50.805 --> 00:07:52.106 position:24% line:83% align:start
why don't you find
yourself a human

00:07:52.139 --> 00:07:53.608 position:7% line:89% align:start
and make him your apprentice?

00:07:53.641 --> 00:07:55.776 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
Hey, that's not a bad idea.

00:07:55.810 --> 00:07:57.778 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Whoa, I was just kidding.

00:07:59.646 --> 00:08:00.982 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
Hey.

00:08:02.183 --> 00:08:04.051 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
I said hey!

00:08:05.886 --> 00:08:08.688 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
What, are you dead or something?

00:08:08.722 --> 00:08:09.823 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Go away.

00:08:09.856 --> 00:08:12.025 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE] Talking.
That means you're alive, then.

00:08:12.058 --> 00:08:13.793 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where's your mom, kid?

00:08:13.827 --> 00:08:14.661 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Go away.

00:08:14.694 --> 00:08:16.663 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
Or your dad. Where's he?

00:08:16.696 --> 00:08:17.631 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Shut up.

00:08:17.664 --> 00:08:18.999 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE]
Answer me!

00:08:19.032 --> 00:08:19.799 position:27% line:89% align:start
Where are they?

00:08:19.833 --> 00:08:21.835 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!

00:08:21.868 --> 00:08:23.870 position:24% line:83% align:start
Say anything else
and I'll kill you!

00:08:23.904 --> 00:08:25.471 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow. Now I'm scared.

00:08:25.504 --> 00:08:27.907 position:13% line:83% align:start
[HOODED FIGURE] Let's take
a look at the little brat.

00:08:29.808 --> 00:08:31.144 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REN grunts]

00:08:34.247 --> 00:08:35.781 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:08:38.183 --> 00:08:39.885 position:30% line:89% align:start
What are you?

00:08:41.553 --> 00:08:42.888 position:41% line:89% align:start
Aagh!

00:08:42.922 --> 00:08:44.089 position:33% line:89% align:start
Not too bad.

00:08:44.123 --> 00:08:46.125 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's just get outta here.

00:08:49.895 --> 00:08:52.797 position:16% line:83% align:start
Hey, kid. How about it?
You wanna come with me?

00:08:52.830 --> 00:08:53.698 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:08:53.731 --> 00:08:54.532 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Huh?!

00:08:54.565 --> 00:08:56.935 position:30% line:83% align:start
Ugh. Don't be
an idiot, Kumatetsu!

