[car horn honks]

00:09:05.109 --> 00:09:07.145 position:27% line:89% align:start
[car horn honks]

00:09:07.879 --> 00:09:22.226 position:24% line:89% align:start
[CROWD chattering]

00:09:22.260 --> 00:09:24.594 position:24% line:83% align:start
[REN] What the--?
I thought I saw...

00:09:27.297 --> 00:09:28.832 position:38% line:89% align:start
A dream?

00:09:30.667 --> 00:09:31.268 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:31.301 --> 00:09:32.169 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're awfully young, kid.

00:09:32.202 --> 00:09:33.170 position:24% line:89% align:start
Are you a runaway?

00:09:33.203 --> 00:09:34.570 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ugh! Lemme go!

00:09:34.603 --> 00:09:36.139 position:19% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't be here
without an adult

00:09:36.173 --> 00:09:37.506 position:13% line:89% align:start
at this time of the night.

00:09:37.540 --> 00:09:38.607 position:33% line:89% align:start
Get off me!

00:09:38.641 --> 00:09:40.177 position:16% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN B] How can we
get a hold of your parents?

00:09:40.210 --> 00:09:41.877 position:16% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN A] We'll have
them come and get you.

00:09:41.911 --> 00:09:42.678 position:33% line:89% align:start
I won't go!

00:09:42.712 --> 00:09:44.513 position:30% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN B]
Come with us, son.

00:09:44.547 --> 00:09:45.881 position:24% line:89% align:start
You can't make me!

00:09:45.915 --> 00:09:46.849 position:41% line:89% align:start
N-No!

00:09:46.882 --> 00:09:47.583 position:30% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN B]
Wait! Stop!

00:09:47.616 --> 00:09:49.151 position:30% line:83% align:start
[POLICEMAN A]
Come back here!

00:09:49.185 --> 00:09:49.885 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REN pants]

