00:10:24.052 --> 00:10:25.787 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, this way.

00:11:06.092 --> 00:11:07.627 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:10.096 --> 00:11:12.899 position:16% line:83% align:start
Where am I? This doesn't
look like Shibuya.

00:11:14.300 --> 00:11:15.835 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:11:26.211 --> 00:11:28.780 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Wait... what?

00:11:28.814 --> 00:11:29.247 position:24% line:89% align:start
[hooves clopping]

00:11:29.281 --> 00:11:30.248 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

00:11:30.282 --> 00:11:31.983 position:24% line:89% align:start
[hooves clopping]

00:11:32.017 --> 00:11:33.718 position:30% line:83% align:start
--[REN gasps]
--CHICO squeaks]

