[REN grunts]

00:11:36.321 --> 00:11:37.856 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:11:39.690 --> 00:11:42.260 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:11:42.294 --> 00:11:44.029 position:30% line:89% align:start
[REN grunting]

00:11:47.932 --> 00:11:48.467 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:53.671 position:16% line:89% align:start
[indistinct chattering]

00:11:58.742 --> 00:12:01.078 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:12:05.316 --> 00:12:06.951 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
What? A wall?

00:12:06.984 --> 00:12:09.153 position:5% line:89% align:start
But I swear I came in this way!

00:12:14.057 --> 00:12:15.625 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's a way out, right?

00:12:38.113 --> 00:12:40.316 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:12:49.057 --> 00:12:52.227 position:30% line:89% align:start
[REN panting]

00:13:02.036 --> 00:13:03.771 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:13:03.804 --> 00:13:04.705 position:16% line:89% align:start
Who's the hairless one?

00:13:04.739 --> 00:13:06.140 position:13% line:83% align:start
--Looks like a human kid.
--Let go of me!

00:13:06.174 --> 00:13:07.442 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's he doin' here?

00:13:07.476 --> 00:13:08.544 position:30% line:89% align:start
What d'ya say?

00:13:08.577 --> 00:13:10.745 position:10% line:83% align:start
Wanna skin 'im and see what
we can get for his hide?

00:13:10.778 --> 00:13:13.414 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yeah, we could, or we could
eat him, or put him in a cage.

00:13:13.447 --> 00:13:14.916 position:24% line:89% align:start
What do you think?

00:13:14.949 --> 00:13:16.450 position:21% line:89% align:start
Help! Someone help!

00:13:16.484 --> 00:13:18.152 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Put the boy down.

00:13:18.186 --> 00:13:20.354 position:30% line:83% align:start
[SCARY BEASTS]
Hm?

00:13:20.388 --> 00:13:23.857 position:30% line:83% align:start
You should be
ashamed of yourselves.

00:13:23.890 --> 00:13:25.926 position:24% line:83% align:start
Pft, stupid monks.
Who needs 'em?

00:13:25.959 --> 00:13:27.495 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Don't pay any attention.

00:13:27.528 --> 00:13:29.497 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're just bullies
who sound a lot tougher

00:13:29.530 --> 00:13:31.264 position:16% line:89% align:start
than they actually are.

00:13:31.298 --> 00:13:33.099 position:5% line:89% align:start
You don't need to be frightened.

00:13:33.133 --> 00:13:34.901 position:16% line:83% align:start
Everything will be fine,
you'll see.

00:13:34.935 --> 00:13:37.804 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm Hyakushubo,
an apprentice monk.

00:13:37.837 --> 00:13:40.507 position:5% line:83% align:start
This is Jutengai, which can only
be reached from your world

00:13:40.540 --> 00:13:42.375 position:24% line:83% align:start
through a certain
pattern of paths.

00:13:42.409 --> 00:13:45.078 position:16% line:83% align:start
Beasts and humans occupy
different worlds, you see.

00:13:45.111 --> 00:13:48.248 position:19% line:83% align:start
Perhaps because we can
become gods and you cannot.

00:13:48.281 --> 00:13:50.950 position:5% line:83% align:start
Poor boy, you must have wandered
here by mistake somehow.

00:13:50.983 --> 00:13:52.051 position:27% line:89% align:start
But don't worry.

00:13:52.084 --> 00:13:54.354 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll see that you get safely
back to your own world.

00:13:54.387 --> 00:13:55.087 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hey!

00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:56.021 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:56.055 --> 00:13:58.224 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] Ha, ha, ha!
You actually came!

00:13:58.257 --> 00:13:58.958 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:13:58.991 --> 00:14:00.192 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:14:00.226 --> 00:14:03.462 position:10% line:83% align:start
Ah, not bad for a human kid!
I knew I was right about you!

00:14:03.495 --> 00:14:04.330 position:35% line:83% align:start
--C'mere!
--[yelps]

00:14:04.363 --> 00:14:05.531 position:21% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?!

00:14:05.564 --> 00:14:07.799 position:24% line:83% align:start
Can't you see he's
lost and frightened?

00:14:07.832 --> 00:14:09.268 position:7% line:89% align:start
We should be kind to the boy!

00:14:09.301 --> 00:14:11.070 position:10% line:89% align:start
You monks are all the same.

00:14:11.103 --> 00:14:12.438 position:16% line:83% align:start
There are more important
things in the world

00:14:12.471 --> 00:14:13.505 position:16% line:89% align:start
than kindness, you know!

00:14:13.539 --> 00:14:15.807 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm just saying you might
try not to be so rough.

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:17.141 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's not like he's gonna break!

00:14:17.175 --> 00:14:19.411 position:13% line:89% align:start
And he's not lost, either.

00:14:19.445 --> 00:14:22.213 position:5% line:89% align:start
He's my apprentice, as of today.

00:14:22.247 --> 00:14:23.781 position:38% line:83% align:start
--What?
--[CHICO squeaks]

00:14:23.815 --> 00:14:26.017 position:7% line:89% align:start
Oh, whoops. Didn't I tell you?

00:14:26.050 --> 00:14:28.353 position:27% line:83% align:start
Your apprentice?
But he's a human child!

00:14:28.386 --> 00:14:31.055 position:7% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] What do I care if
he's a human or a toilet brush?

00:14:31.089 --> 00:14:32.991 position:21% line:83% align:start
An apprentice is an
apprentice, got it?

00:14:33.024 --> 00:14:34.392 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

00:14:34.425 --> 00:14:36.793 position:19% line:83% align:start
What's he doing here?
I told you I was kidding!

00:14:36.827 --> 00:14:38.496 position:5% line:89% align:start
Tatara, tell me what's going on.

00:14:38.529 --> 00:14:40.797 position:24% line:83% align:start
The lord told him
that if he really wants

00:14:40.831 --> 00:14:41.733 position:21% line:89% align:start
to be the successor,

00:14:41.765 --> 00:14:43.867 position:24% line:83% align:start
he should start by
finding an apprentice.

00:14:43.900 --> 00:14:45.503 position:10% line:89% align:start
He's not like Iozen, though.

00:14:45.536 --> 00:14:47.271 position:24% line:83% align:start
I mean boys aren't
exactly lining up

00:14:47.304 --> 00:14:49.406 position:27% line:83% align:start
for the right to
call him "Master."

00:14:49.439 --> 00:14:52.009 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, anyway, we were
out amusing ourselves

00:14:52.042 --> 00:14:54.244 position:13% line:83% align:start
in the human world when we
came across this youngling.

00:14:54.278 --> 00:14:55.412 position:7% line:89% align:start
And, what, you kidnapped him?

00:14:55.445 --> 00:14:57.481 position:21% line:83% align:start
We didn't take him.
He followed us.

00:14:57.514 --> 00:14:58.982 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Then do the responsible thing

00:14:59.016 --> 00:15:00.950 position:24% line:83% align:start
and take him back
where he belongs.

00:15:00.983 --> 00:15:01.784 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why should I?!

00:15:01.817 --> 00:15:03.287 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's so wrong with
showing interest

00:15:03.320 --> 00:15:04.854 position:13% line:89% align:start
in a promising youngster?!

00:15:04.887 --> 00:15:06.222 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:15:07.990 --> 00:15:08.492 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on!

00:15:08.525 --> 00:15:10.427 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REN gasps]

00:15:10.460 --> 00:15:13.095 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] What is he
thinking? This is crazy.

00:15:13.129 --> 00:15:15.531 position:19% line:83% align:start
I never knew he wanted
an apprentice so badly.

00:15:15.564 --> 00:15:17.867 position:33% line:83% align:start
He doesn't.
This is about competition.

00:15:17.900 --> 00:15:19.969 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's about winning
against Iozen.

00:15:20.002 --> 00:15:21.070 position:21% line:89% align:start
You know how he is.

00:15:21.103 --> 00:15:22.204 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, I do.

00:15:22.238 --> 00:15:25.007 position:13% line:83% align:start
Being lord of a world and
then ascending to godhood

00:15:25.041 --> 00:15:26.442 position:30% line:83% align:start
probably means
very little to him.

00:15:26.475 --> 00:15:29.445 position:21% line:83% align:start
Heh! Can you imagine
if he did reincarnate?

00:15:29.478 --> 00:15:31.146 position:27% line:83% align:start
What would he be
the god of, do you think?

00:15:31.179 --> 00:15:34.883 position:19% line:83% align:start
Scrub brushes, maybe?
Oh, or perhaps toilets?

00:15:34.916 --> 00:15:37.952 position:13% line:83% align:start
Honestly, my main concern
is for the human child.

00:15:37.986 --> 00:15:40.388 position:21% line:83% align:start
How will he fare in
Kumatetsu's custody?

00:15:40.422 --> 00:15:43.191 position:7% line:89% align:start
I don't know. Not my problem.

00:15:44.326 --> 00:15:45.860 position:24% line:89% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO sighs]

00:16:00.174 --> 00:16:01.509 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
Huh...?

00:16:06.980 --> 00:16:09.249 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
What do you mean apprentice?

00:16:09.283 --> 00:16:10.517 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
It means from now on,

00:16:10.551 --> 00:16:12.286 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm the one who's
gonna feed you.

00:16:12.319 --> 00:16:14.921 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
It's not like I asked you to.

00:16:14.954 --> 00:16:17.123 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
You sleep there.

00:16:17.157 --> 00:16:18.525 position:35% line:89% align:start
One thing.

00:16:18.559 --> 00:16:20.893 position:24% line:83% align:start
I hate crybabies.
No use for them.

00:16:20.927 --> 00:16:22.496 position:7% line:89% align:start
You cry and I'll kick you out.

00:16:22.529 --> 00:16:23.497 position:33% line:89% align:start
I won't cry.

00:16:23.530 --> 00:16:24.997 position:13% line:89% align:start
Then we should get along.

00:16:25.031 --> 00:16:26.099 position:19% line:89% align:start
But that doesn't mean

00:16:26.132 --> 00:16:28.301 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm saying I'll be your
apprentice, because I'm not.

00:16:28.334 --> 00:16:30.069 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
So why'd you follow me?

00:16:30.103 --> 00:16:31.337 position:30% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:16:31.371 --> 00:16:33.172 position:27% line:83% align:start
You don't really
have to say it.

00:16:33.206 --> 00:16:34.974 position:5% line:89% align:start
I know you've got nowhere to go.

00:16:35.007 --> 00:16:36.609 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
You feeling sorry for me?

00:16:36.642 --> 00:16:37.744 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why would I?!

00:16:37.777 --> 00:16:40.546 position:19% line:83% align:start
So you gotta make your
own way, what's the big deal?

00:16:40.580 --> 00:16:44.450 position:16% line:83% align:start
Plenty of people do it.
Doesn't make you special.

00:16:46.486 --> 00:16:48.521 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
What's your name, anyway?

00:16:49.622 --> 00:16:50.523 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm not telling.

00:16:50.556 --> 00:16:51.356 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:51.390 --> 00:16:53.191 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REN]
That's personal information.

00:16:53.225 --> 00:16:55.994 position:19% line:89% align:start
Fine! How old are ya?

00:17:00.999 --> 00:17:02.267 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:17:02.300 --> 00:17:04.436 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:17:04.469 --> 00:17:07.272 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, now you're a
nine-year-old named Kyuta.

00:17:07.305 --> 00:17:09.674 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hey! You can't just
make up a name for me!

00:17:09.708 --> 00:17:12.276 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Really? Sounds like I just did.

00:17:12.309 --> 00:17:14.646 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well. I'm going to
sleep now, Kyuta.

00:17:14.679 --> 00:17:16.213 position:35% line:89% align:start
Goodnight.

00:17:17.415 --> 00:17:18.949 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA sighs]

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:37.735 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S MOTHER]
Ren.

00:17:37.768 --> 00:17:39.302 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Huh?

00:17:39.335 --> 00:17:42.238 position:21% line:83% align:start
I made a ham omelet.
I know how much you love them.

00:17:42.272 --> 00:17:44.474 position:30% line:83% align:start
You should eat
before it gets cold.

00:17:46.376 --> 00:17:47.710 position:41% line:89% align:start
'Kay.

00:17:57.587 --> 00:18:07.596 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA sobs quietly]

00:18:10.699 --> 00:18:14.336 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yawns]

00:18:20.275 --> 00:18:22.311 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:18:24.245 --> 00:18:25.647 position:33% line:89% align:start
He ran away.

00:18:25.681 --> 00:18:29.016 position:27% line:83% align:start
No big surprise.
I thought he might.

00:18:29.050 --> 00:18:31.085 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yawns]

00:18:38.092 --> 00:18:40.361 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:40.394 --> 00:18:42.296 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:18:42.330 --> 00:18:44.799 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Not gone after all!

00:18:44.832 --> 00:18:46.367 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

00:18:49.403 --> 00:18:50.337 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[KYUTA screams]
--[CHICO squeals]

00:18:50.370 --> 00:18:51.506 position:38% line:89% align:start
Wha--?!

00:18:51.539 --> 00:18:53.139 position:27% line:89% align:start
Breakfast time!

00:18:53.173 --> 00:18:55.542 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Stop already!

00:18:55.575 --> 00:18:57.611 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
How long are you gonna pout?

00:18:57.644 --> 00:18:59.446 position:27% line:83% align:start
Guess you're not
a morning person, huh?

00:18:59.479 --> 00:19:01.548 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, go on then. Eat up.

00:19:01.581 --> 00:19:03.083 position:16% line:89% align:start
Eggs fresh as they get.

00:19:03.116 --> 00:19:05.452 position:30% line:83% align:start
I eat 'em raw.
They're best that way.

00:19:05.485 --> 00:19:07.521 position:13% line:83% align:start
What are you waiting for?
Not hungry?

00:19:07.554 --> 00:19:08.588 position:27% line:89% align:start
Of course I am!

00:19:08.622 --> 00:19:09.589 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well then, eat!

00:19:09.623 --> 00:19:11.223 position:19% line:89% align:start
I don't eat eggs raw!

00:19:11.258 --> 00:19:12.291 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Huh?

00:19:12.325 --> 00:19:13.793 position:33% line:83% align:start
How can you?
It's disgusting.

00:19:13.827 --> 00:19:15.629 position:21% line:83% align:start
You don't know what
you're talking about!

00:19:15.662 --> 00:19:17.463 position:33% line:89% align:start
Just watch!

00:19:17.864 --> 00:19:20.232 position:21% line:89% align:start
[slurping, chomping]

00:19:20.266 --> 00:19:21.066 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hah!

00:19:21.100 --> 00:19:22.201 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Yup. Disgusting.

00:19:22.234 --> 00:19:24.069 position:7% line:83% align:start
--You're gonna eat it, anyway!
--Ew! Close your mouth!

00:19:24.103 --> 00:19:25.604 position:10% line:89% align:start
An apprentice can't say no!

00:19:25.638 --> 00:19:27.206 position:13% line:89% align:start
I am not your apprentice!

00:19:27.239 --> 00:19:28.340 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sit down and eat!

00:19:28.374 --> 00:19:29.542 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:19:29.575 --> 00:19:31.710 position:13% line:83% align:start
If you won't eat the food
I put in front of you, I'll...

00:19:31.744 --> 00:19:33.178 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah? You'll what?

00:19:33.212 --> 00:19:35.213 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
I'll shove it down your throat!

00:19:35.247 --> 00:19:36.214 position:27% line:89% align:start
This is foolish.

00:19:36.247 --> 00:19:37.716 position:19% line:83% align:start
--Leave the boy alone.
--[KYUTA] I hate you!

00:19:37.750 --> 00:19:39.183 position:10% line:89% align:start
Wait, I've got another idea.

00:19:39.217 --> 00:19:40.786 position:24% line:83% align:start
Take the kid back
where he belongs.

00:19:40.819 --> 00:19:43.221 position:13% line:89% align:start
You'll both be better off!

00:19:43.254 --> 00:19:43.923 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where'd he go?

00:19:43.956 --> 00:19:46.090 position:5% line:89% align:start
I hate you and your stupid eggs!

00:19:46.124 --> 00:19:48.426 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Get back here! Kyuta!

00:19:48.459 --> 00:19:50.328 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TATARA, HYAKUSHUBO]
Kyuta?

00:19:51.663 --> 00:19:52.664 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hey!

00:19:52.697 --> 00:19:54.832 position:21% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] I'm not ever
gonna be your apprentice!

00:19:54.866 --> 00:19:57.235 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Stop running, brat!

00:19:57.268 --> 00:19:58.168 position:24% line:83% align:start
[PAINTER BEAST B]
Over that way a little.

00:19:58.202 --> 00:20:01.573 position:24% line:83% align:start
[PAINTER BEAST A]
Okay. Uh... like this?

00:20:01.606 --> 00:20:02.574 position:19% line:89% align:start
Does this look right?

00:20:02.607 --> 00:20:03.808 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU yells]

00:20:03.841 --> 00:20:06.544 position:21% line:89% align:start
Which way? [growls]

00:20:06.578 --> 00:20:09.681 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] There has to be
a way back home somewhere...

00:20:14.718 --> 00:20:15.719 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clanging]

00:20:15.752 --> 00:20:17.287 position:10% line:89% align:start
[BLACKSMITH BEASTS grunting]

00:20:22.459 --> 00:20:23.327 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

00:20:23.360 --> 00:20:24.895 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE CLERK BEAST]
Here you go, dear.

00:20:24.928 --> 00:20:26.897 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yum. Do you want some?

00:20:26.930 --> 00:20:28.865 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, alright!
That's fine by me.

00:20:28.899 --> 00:20:30.433 position:21% line:89% align:start
Then it's all mine!

00:20:30.466 --> 00:20:32.301 position:16% line:83% align:start
Let's see, I think I'll
start with an orange.

00:20:32.335 --> 00:20:33.269 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gulps]

00:20:33.302 --> 00:20:34.470 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ahhh...

00:20:34.503 --> 00:20:35.705 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:20:35.739 --> 00:20:36.672 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
Nope. Changed my mind.

00:20:36.706 --> 00:20:39.442 position:21% line:83% align:start
It'll be better if I
start with the cherry.

00:20:39.475 --> 00:20:40.443 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ahhh...

00:20:40.476 --> 00:20:41.877 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:20:41.911 --> 00:20:44.347 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Jiromaru. Look! There's Father.

00:20:44.380 --> 00:20:46.349 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
Huh? Hey, Dad!

00:20:46.382 --> 00:20:49.819 position:7% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN] Ichirohiko, Jiromaru.
Are you training hard, boys?

00:20:49.852 --> 00:20:50.987 position:41% line:83% align:start
--Yep.
--Yes.

00:20:51.020 --> 00:20:53.823 position:13% line:83% align:start
Would you demonstrate more
techniques for us sometime?

00:20:53.856 --> 00:20:56.324 position:13% line:89% align:start
Of course. How about now?

00:20:56.358 --> 00:20:57.793 position:35% line:83% align:start
--Master.
--[JIROMARU, ICHIROHIKO gasp]

00:20:57.827 --> 00:20:58.861 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Never mind.

00:20:58.894 --> 00:21:00.695 position:19% line:83% align:start
It looks like it will
have to wait until later.

00:21:00.729 --> 00:21:02.297 position:21% line:89% align:start
You always say that!

00:21:02.330 --> 00:21:02.932 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay!

00:21:02.965 --> 00:21:05.333 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, boys.

00:21:05.367 --> 00:21:06.701 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh...?

00:21:08.403 --> 00:21:09.604 position:35% line:89% align:start
Kumatetsu.

00:21:09.638 --> 00:21:11.806 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

00:21:11.840 --> 00:21:13.074 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh. Hi, Iozen.

00:21:13.108 --> 00:21:16.210 position:5% line:83% align:start
From what I hear, you've finally
found yourself an apprentice.

00:21:16.243 --> 00:21:18.813 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, but I lost
track of him somehow.

00:21:18.847 --> 00:21:20.214 position:21% line:89% align:start
You seen him around?

00:21:20.247 --> 00:21:21.816 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's a little kid.
About this high.

00:21:21.850 --> 00:21:22.817 position:30% line:89% align:start
He's a child?

00:21:22.851 --> 00:21:25.219 position:19% line:83% align:start
But you're practically
still a child yourself.

00:21:25.252 --> 00:21:27.287 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Tch. Aw, what do you know?

00:21:27.321 --> 00:21:29.423 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm speaking as the
father of two children.

00:21:29.456 --> 00:21:30.557 position:30% line:89% align:start
It isn't easy.

00:21:30.591 --> 00:21:32.793 position:5% line:83% align:start
You might not have what it takes
to be a good guardian.

00:21:32.826 --> 00:21:34.294 position:21% line:89% align:start
Not everybody does.

00:21:34.328 --> 00:21:35.562 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Yeah, whatever.

00:21:35.596 --> 00:21:38.899 position:7% line:83% align:start
When I decide to do something,
it gets done one way or another.

00:21:38.932 --> 00:21:40.734 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now, where is that Kyuta?

00:21:40.768 --> 00:21:43.771 position:10% line:83% align:start
He's quicker than I thought
he'd be, for a human kid.

00:21:43.804 --> 00:21:45.005 position:21% line:89% align:start
Wait, what was that?

00:21:45.039 --> 00:21:48.541 position:5% line:83% align:start
You aren't actually saying that
your apprentice is a human?

00:21:48.574 --> 00:21:49.542 position:21% line:83% align:start
[APPRENTICE BEAST B]
Master!

00:21:49.575 --> 00:21:51.377 position:38% line:83% align:start
Ow! Hey!
Let me go!

00:21:51.411 --> 00:21:52.378 position:27% line:83% align:start
[BEAST WOMAN A]
A human?

00:21:52.412 --> 00:21:54.247 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN B]
What is it doing in our world?

00:21:54.280 --> 00:21:56.349 position:21% line:89% align:start
A human boy? Really?

00:21:56.382 --> 00:21:58.451 position:24% line:83% align:start
What's one of them
doing in Jutengai?

00:21:58.484 --> 00:22:00.219 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ah! There you are!

00:22:00.253 --> 00:22:01.621 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Listen to me, Kumatetsu.

00:22:01.654 --> 00:22:04.256 position:21% line:83% align:start
You don't know what
you're getting yourself into.

00:22:04.289 --> 00:22:06.959 position:10% line:83% align:start
What are you talking about?
I'm just taking an apprentice.

00:22:06.993 --> 00:22:09.528 position:19% line:83% align:start
You know why we don't
live among the humans.

00:22:09.562 --> 00:22:10.529 position:24% line:89% align:start
They appear weak,

00:22:10.562 --> 00:22:12.564 position:16% line:83% align:start
but they harbor Darkness
within their hearts.

00:22:12.597 --> 00:22:15.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
What if this boy gets
possessed by that Darkness?

00:22:15.300 --> 00:22:16.635 position:21% line:83% align:start
Have you to stopped
to consider that?

00:22:16.668 --> 00:22:18.837 position:21% line:83% align:start
He could grow up to
become a terrible monster.

00:22:18.870 --> 00:22:21.840 position:30% line:83% align:start
Monster? Heh!
He's just a scrawny kid.

00:22:21.873 --> 00:22:23.041 position:5% line:89% align:start
There's no monster in that boy.

00:22:23.075 --> 00:22:26.578 position:7% line:83% align:start
Think! If you do this, it will
affect more than just you.

00:22:26.611 --> 00:22:29.246 position:16% line:83% align:start
I decide what to do with
my own apprentice, got it?

00:22:29.280 --> 00:22:30.782 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm warning you, don't do it!

00:22:30.816 --> 00:22:32.684 position:21% line:83% align:start
For the sake of all
Beasts in Jutengai!

00:22:32.718 --> 00:22:36.654 position:27% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS chatter]

00:22:36.688 --> 00:22:38.255 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ha, just listen to you.

00:22:38.289 --> 00:22:39.757 position:7% line:89% align:start
"For the sake of all Beasts!"

00:22:39.791 --> 00:22:41.759 position:19% line:83% align:start
Like you think you're
already the next lord.

00:22:41.792 --> 00:22:43.327 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

00:22:44.595 --> 00:22:46.931 position:5% line:83% align:start
If you're so worried about what
I'm doing with my apprentice,

00:22:46.964 --> 00:22:47.865 position:19% line:89% align:start
why don't you stop me?

00:22:47.898 --> 00:22:50.000 position:21% line:83% align:start
We can fight for the
lordship right now.

00:22:50.034 --> 00:22:50.868 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:22:50.901 --> 00:22:52.837 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN D]
Iozen versus Kumatetsu!

00:22:52.870 --> 00:22:53.938 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN E]
Now there's a battle!

00:22:53.971 --> 00:22:54.939 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN F]
Make room, people!

00:22:54.972 --> 00:22:56.941 position:27% line:83% align:start
[BEAST WOMAN C]
The winner gets the lordship?

00:22:57.975 --> 00:22:59.877 position:10% line:89% align:start
Quick, we need to stop him!

00:22:59.910 --> 00:23:01.544 position:19% line:89% align:start
Crush him, Kumatetsu!

00:23:01.578 --> 00:23:02.545 position:27% line:89% align:start
I bet on Iozen.

00:23:02.579 --> 00:23:03.646 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, so do I.

00:23:03.680 --> 00:23:04.748 position:27% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh, me too.

00:23:04.781 --> 00:23:06.750 position:16% line:83% align:start
If we all bet the same,
there's no bet!

00:23:06.783 --> 00:23:07.817 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN sighs]

00:23:07.851 --> 00:23:08.718 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
I'll take that.

00:23:08.752 --> 00:23:10.553 position:21% line:89% align:start
Stand back, you two.

00:23:16.760 --> 00:23:18.293 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN G]
Kumatetsu's a disgrace.

00:23:18.327 --> 00:23:19.596 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN H]
What does he think he's doing?

00:23:19.629 --> 00:23:20.764 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN I]
He has no manners!

00:23:20.797 --> 00:23:22.431 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN J]
Be more like Iozen!

00:23:22.464 --> 00:23:24.768 position:27% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS booing]

00:23:24.801 --> 00:23:26.668 position:41% line:83% align:start
--Hey!
--Follow fight etiquette!

00:23:26.702 --> 00:23:28.670 position:19% line:83% align:start
He couldn't care less
about fight etiquette.

00:23:28.704 --> 00:23:29.738 position:35% line:89% align:start
That fool.

00:23:29.772 --> 00:23:32.808 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's managed to turn
the whole crowd against him.

00:23:34.110 --> 00:23:35.978 position:30% line:83% align:start
A sword fight?
Is someone gonna die?

00:23:36.011 --> 00:23:38.380 position:21% line:83% align:start
The lord forbids us
to unsheathe our swords.

00:23:38.413 --> 00:23:39.915 position:19% line:83% align:start
They're even tied shut
in the scabbards

00:23:39.948 --> 00:23:41.884 position:5% line:89% align:start
to prevent anyone from doing so.

00:23:41.917 --> 00:23:43.886 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, okay.

00:23:43.919 --> 00:23:45.087 position:10% line:89% align:start
[APPRENTICE BEAST B grunts]

00:23:45.120 --> 00:23:47.589 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey! Stop! Get back here!

00:23:47.623 --> 00:23:48.422 position:33% line:89% align:start
Where is he?

00:23:48.456 --> 00:23:50.424 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

00:24:02.870 --> 00:24:06.374 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

00:24:10.545 --> 00:24:11.612 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TATARA laughs]

00:24:11.646 --> 00:24:13.648 position:16% line:89% align:start
A fool. A complete fool.

00:24:13.681 --> 00:24:16.050 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] It's how he
intimidates his opponent.

00:24:16.083 --> 00:24:17.651 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

00:24:17.684 --> 00:24:19.020 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:24:24.825 --> 00:24:25.659 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN K]
Whoa!

00:24:25.692 --> 00:24:27.427 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN L]
Way to dodge him, Iozen!

00:24:27.460 --> 00:24:28.929 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:24:28.962 --> 00:24:31.464 position:19% line:83% align:start
Challenging the other
guy to hit him now?

00:24:31.498 --> 00:24:34.968 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

00:24:35.001 --> 00:24:37.536 position:27% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN grunting]

00:24:37.570 --> 00:24:38.637 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:24:38.672 --> 00:24:39.840 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:24:39.873 --> 00:24:40.807 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:24:40.841 --> 00:24:42.374 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU groans]

00:24:45.845 --> 00:24:46.378 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:24:46.412 --> 00:24:47.546 position:38% line:83% align:start
--Yeah!
--All right!

00:24:47.580 --> 00:24:48.914 position:38% line:83% align:start
--Idiot!
--[laughs]

00:24:51.450 --> 00:24:52.651 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:24:52.685 --> 00:24:53.986 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:24:54.019 --> 00:24:55.087 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:24:55.120 --> 00:24:59.992 position:27% line:83% align:start
--[BEASTS cheer]
--[KUMATETSU groans]

00:25:00.025 --> 00:25:04.395 position:21% line:89% align:start
[cheering continues]

00:25:04.429 --> 00:25:05.630 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Hmm?

00:25:05.663 --> 00:25:07.933 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:25:10.768 --> 00:25:12.670 position:21% line:89% align:start
We're not done yet!

00:25:19.644 --> 00:25:20.879 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:25:20.912 --> 00:25:23.147 position:33% line:83% align:start
--He's huge!
--[JIROMARU gasps]

00:25:23.181 --> 00:25:25.083 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't worry, boys.

00:25:31.822 --> 00:25:32.856 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:25:32.891 --> 00:25:34.858 position:38% line:83% align:start
[BEASTS]
Ready?

00:25:34.892 --> 00:25:35.726 position:41% line:89% align:start
Fight!

00:25:35.759 --> 00:25:36.660 position:16% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU, IOZEN grunt]

00:25:36.693 --> 00:25:38.028 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

00:25:39.529 --> 00:25:41.498 position:13% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU, IOZEN grunt]
--[BEASTS cheer]

00:25:43.166 --> 00:25:45.969 position:13% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU, IOZEN grunt]
--[BEASTS cheer]

00:25:46.003 --> 00:25:47.671 position:16% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU, IOZEN grunt]

00:25:47.704 --> 00:25:49.840 position:21% line:89% align:start
[cheering continues]

00:25:49.873 --> 00:25:52.142 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN growls]

00:25:54.710 --> 00:25:57.513 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:25:57.546 --> 00:25:59.448 position:27% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN grunting]

00:25:59.482 --> 00:26:05.955 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:26:05.988 --> 00:26:07.023 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN M]
Get out of the way!

00:26:07.056 --> 00:26:08.958 position:13% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN N] Iozen can't
seem to push him back!

00:26:08.991 --> 00:26:11.227 position:10% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN O] He's not going
to lose the fight, is he?

00:26:11.260 --> 00:26:12.862 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:26:12.895 --> 00:26:15.463 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN grunts]

00:26:15.497 --> 00:26:17.166 position:13% line:89% align:start
Iozen, we believe in you!

00:26:17.199 --> 00:26:18.500 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN P]
Iozen!

00:26:18.533 --> 00:26:25.107 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CROWD]
Iozen! Iozen! Iozen! Iozen!

00:26:25.141 --> 00:26:26.641 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
The crowd.

00:26:26.675 --> 00:26:28.977 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're all cheering
for the other guy.

00:26:30.246 --> 00:26:32.013 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
No one's rooting for him.

00:26:32.047 --> 00:26:33.181 position:27% line:89% align:start
He's all alone.

00:26:33.214 --> 00:26:36.685 position:21% line:89% align:start
[chanting continues]

00:26:36.718 --> 00:26:42.223 position:19% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN grunts, growls]

00:26:42.257 --> 00:26:44.893 position:13% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls, gasps]

00:26:47.728 --> 00:26:49.064 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:26:50.597 --> 00:26:55.270 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:26:55.303 --> 00:26:58.005 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Ugh. [growls]

00:26:58.038 --> 00:26:59.273 position:19% line:89% align:start
You want to continue?

00:26:59.306 --> 00:27:00.541 position:30% line:89% align:start
Keep fighting.

00:27:00.574 --> 00:27:03.177 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm not stopping
till I beat you!

00:27:03.210 --> 00:27:04.510 position:13% line:89% align:start
I think you've had enough.

00:27:04.544 --> 00:27:07.680 position:13% line:89% align:start
No. Not yet. I'm not done!

00:27:07.714 --> 00:27:09.116 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU yells]

00:27:10.650 --> 00:27:11.986 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:27:13.886 --> 00:27:15.922 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU pants]
--[BEAST MAN P] Iozen!

00:27:17.023 --> 00:27:22.261 position:19% line:83% align:start
[BEASTS] Iozen! Iozen!
Iozen! Iozen! Iozen!

00:27:22.295 --> 00:27:27.033 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU pants]

00:27:27.066 --> 00:27:33.272 position:10% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU, IOZEN grunting]

00:27:35.674 --> 00:27:36.575 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:27:36.608 --> 00:27:38.311 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah! You show him, Dad!

00:27:38.344 --> 00:27:41.180 position:24% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheering]

00:27:41.214 --> 00:27:42.014 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:27:42.047 --> 00:27:43.582 position:35% line:89% align:start
Kumatetsu.

00:27:47.285 --> 00:27:49.287 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:27:49.321 --> 00:27:54.226 position:38% line:89% align:start
[growls]

00:27:54.259 --> 00:27:55.559 position:24% line:89% align:start
Fight, Kumatetsu!

00:27:55.593 --> 00:27:58.296 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU gasps]

00:27:58.330 --> 00:27:59.431 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN Q]
Who was that?

00:27:59.464 --> 00:28:01.166 position:5% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN R] Someone's actually
rooting for that loser?

00:28:01.199 --> 00:28:02.700 position:27% line:83% align:start
[BEAST WOMAN E]
Who would do that?

00:28:02.733 --> 00:28:04.568 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Huh?

00:28:04.602 --> 00:28:06.537 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't let him win!

00:28:07.605 --> 00:28:09.140 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kyu--

00:28:09.173 --> 00:28:10.708 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:28:12.943 --> 00:28:13.878 position:33% line:89% align:start
[BOTH gasp]

00:28:13.911 --> 00:28:15.312 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all over!

00:28:19.350 --> 00:28:20.583 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
That's enough.

00:28:20.617 --> 00:28:21.618 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:28:21.651 --> 00:28:23.988 position:38% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
Of course, Lord.

00:28:27.024 --> 00:28:28.825 position:27% line:83% align:start
[LORD] I'd like
an explanation for this.

00:28:28.858 --> 00:28:30.927 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's not time for the battle.

00:28:30.960 --> 00:28:34.230 position:13% line:83% align:start
Nor will it be until I've
decided what god I will become.

00:28:34.264 --> 00:28:35.598 position:27% line:89% align:start
Forgive me, sir.

00:28:35.632 --> 00:28:37.367 position:5% line:89% align:start
Kumatetsu brought a human here.

00:28:37.400 --> 00:28:38.536 position:13% line:89% align:start
I ask that he be punished.

00:28:38.568 --> 00:28:42.138 position:10% line:83% align:start
Huh. Judging by his current
state of unconsciousness,

00:28:42.172 --> 00:28:45.108 position:13% line:83% align:start
I would say you've already
seen to that without my help.

00:28:45.141 --> 00:28:46.276 position:35% line:89% align:start
Whatever.

00:28:46.309 --> 00:28:50.013 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't care what you say,
Kyuta is my apprentice now.

00:28:50.046 --> 00:28:52.815 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh-ho! I guess the
punishment didn't take.

00:28:52.848 --> 00:28:54.817 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're going to allow
him to keep the boy?

00:28:54.850 --> 00:28:57.920 position:7% line:83% align:start
I don't believe he can handle
such a responsibility.

00:28:57.953 --> 00:28:59.922 position:27% line:83% align:start
I will take the
responsibility.

00:28:59.955 --> 00:29:01.824 position:24% line:83% align:start
After all, it was
at my instruction

00:29:01.857 --> 00:29:03.258 position:16% line:89% align:start
he sought an apprentice.

00:29:03.292 --> 00:29:05.194 position:7% line:83% align:start
But if the Darkness he carries
should consume him--

00:29:05.227 --> 00:29:06.762 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Not every human is ultimately

00:29:06.795 --> 00:29:07.996 position:13% line:89% align:start
possessed by the Darkness.

00:29:08.030 --> 00:29:09.865 position:27% line:83% align:start
Some are able to
escape that fate.

00:29:09.898 --> 00:29:11.100 position:33% line:89% align:start
Sir, please!

00:29:11.133 --> 00:29:13.634 position:7% line:83% align:start
Why are you always so lenient
when it comes to Kumatetsu?

00:29:13.668 --> 00:29:14.702 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
We're finished here.

00:29:14.735 --> 00:29:16.405 position:27% line:83% align:start
There's nothing
more to discuss.

00:29:16.438 --> 00:29:17.972 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS groan]

00:29:19.408 --> 00:29:22.076 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's it, then. The lord
was generous with you.

00:29:22.110 --> 00:29:24.145 position:13% line:89% align:start
I hope you appreciate it.

00:29:26.714 --> 00:29:30.985 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU groans]

00:29:31.018 --> 00:29:32.353 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:29:43.231 --> 00:29:46.700 position:13% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts, yells]

00:29:52.472 --> 00:29:53.974 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
You're really strong.

00:29:54.007 --> 00:29:56.877 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hah. What fight
were you watching?

00:29:56.910 --> 00:30:00.746 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] If you can make me
strong like you are, then okay.

00:30:00.779 --> 00:30:02.882 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll stay here and
be your apprentice.

00:30:02.915 --> 00:30:04.683 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hmph. Yeah, sure.

00:30:04.717 --> 00:30:06.819 position:10% line:89% align:start
You'll just run away again.

00:30:08.355 --> 00:30:11.790 position:16% line:83% align:start
These eggs aren't rotten
or anything, right?

00:30:22.001 --> 00:30:23.269 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

00:30:23.302 --> 00:30:25.004 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA retches]

00:30:25.037 --> 00:30:26.939 position:33% line:89% align:start
Wow. Yummy.

00:30:30.276 --> 00:30:33.179 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:30:33.212 --> 00:30:34.712 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now we're in business!

00:30:34.746 --> 00:30:37.749 position:21% line:83% align:start
I hope you are ready
for some serious training!

00:30:37.782 --> 00:30:41.085 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:30:41.119 --> 00:30:42.187 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA retches]

00:30:42.220 --> 00:30:46.024 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU laughs]

00:30:52.763 --> 00:30:54.098 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Huh?

00:30:55.832 --> 00:30:58.101 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well. You clean up
nicely, Kyuta.

00:30:58.135 --> 00:31:00.237 position:38% line:89% align:start
Shut up.

00:31:00.271 --> 00:31:02.773 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now. Watch and learn.

00:31:06.343 --> 00:31:08.245 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU grunts]
--[KYUTA gasps]

00:31:15.018 --> 00:31:16.520 position:21% line:89% align:start
Eh, that wasn't bad.

00:31:16.553 --> 00:31:19.423 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Got that? Your turn.

00:31:19.456 --> 00:31:20.524 position:24% line:89% align:start
What do you mean?

00:31:20.557 --> 00:31:23.092 position:19% line:89% align:start
Go on. Give it a try.

00:31:28.532 --> 00:31:32.068 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yah! Nnyah!

00:31:32.101 --> 00:31:33.035 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:31:33.069 --> 00:31:34.403 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TATARA laughs]

00:31:39.242 --> 00:31:41.943 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yah! Ugh! Chyah!

00:31:41.978 --> 00:31:43.812 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ow! Ow-ow-ow!

00:31:43.845 --> 00:31:45.181 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:31:47.583 --> 00:31:50.986 position:16% line:89% align:start
Stop it. That's enough!

00:31:51.019 --> 00:31:53.288 position:10% line:89% align:start
Well? What am I doing wrong?

00:31:53.321 --> 00:31:56.291 position:19% line:83% align:start
Heh! You crack me up!
What aren't you doing wrong?

00:31:56.324 --> 00:31:58.860 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's my first time, okay?
I'll get better!

00:31:58.893 --> 00:32:00.462 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TATARA cackles]

00:32:00.495 --> 00:32:03.465 position:19% line:83% align:start
"It's my first time."
No, you don't say!

00:32:03.498 --> 00:32:04.633 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[TATARA laughs]
--[KUMATETSU] Hey! Shut up!

00:32:04.666 --> 00:32:07.269 position:13% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] He can't just
look at you and then do it.

00:32:07.302 --> 00:32:09.237 position:21% line:83% align:start
You have to explain
how it's done.

00:32:09.271 --> 00:32:10.305 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Explain?

00:32:10.338 --> 00:32:13.140 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] That's what
it means to be the master.

00:32:15.943 --> 00:32:17.945 position:7% line:89% align:start
Then I'll explain. Listen up.

00:32:17.978 --> 00:32:20.814 position:27% line:83% align:start
First, you grip
your sword. 'Kay?

00:32:20.848 --> 00:32:23.951 position:24% line:83% align:start
Then it's a woosh
and a bang!

00:32:23.984 --> 00:32:25.886 position:38% line:89% align:start
Got it?

00:32:25.919 --> 00:32:28.555 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ahh... I-I don't know.

00:32:28.589 --> 00:32:30.190 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's easy.

00:32:30.224 --> 00:32:34.827 position:21% line:83% align:start
Grip! And then it's
just a woosh and a bang.

00:32:34.861 --> 00:32:35.828 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay?

00:32:35.862 --> 00:32:38.197 position:35% line:89% align:start
G-Grip it?

00:32:38.231 --> 00:32:39.533 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, like this.

00:32:39.566 --> 00:32:40.501 position:38% line:89% align:start
Grrr-ip!

00:32:40.534 --> 00:32:41.034 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA growls]

00:32:41.067 --> 00:32:42.935 position:21% line:89% align:start
No, no, no, no, no.

00:32:42.969 --> 00:32:44.904 position:33% line:89% align:start
Grrr-- See?

00:32:44.937 --> 00:32:45.938 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Gri--

00:32:45.972 --> 00:32:47.607 position:33% line:89% align:start
No, no, no!

00:32:47.640 --> 00:32:49.342 position:30% line:89% align:start
Grriiip! Yeah?

00:32:49.375 --> 00:32:50.076 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Grip!

00:32:50.109 --> 00:32:51.611 position:27% line:89% align:start
No, no, no, no!

00:32:51.644 --> 00:32:53.413 position:33% line:83% align:start
--GRRRIP IT!
--[TATARA slurps]

00:32:53.446 --> 00:32:54.447 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[KYUTA] GRRRIP IT!
--[TATARA slurps]

00:32:54.480 --> 00:32:55.515 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
GRIP IT!

00:32:55.548 --> 00:32:56.215 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
GRIP IT!

00:32:56.249 --> 00:32:58.016 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
No, no, no, no!

00:32:58.050 --> 00:33:01.820 position:16% line:83% align:start
This is beginner stuff!
How hard can it possibly be?!

00:33:04.590 --> 00:33:05.391 position:38% line:89% align:start
[growls]

00:33:05.425 --> 00:33:06.358 position:21% line:89% align:start
This isn't working!

00:33:06.391 --> 00:33:07.560 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

00:33:07.593 --> 00:33:09.461 position:5% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] I can't learn if you're
not gonna teach me right!

00:33:09.494 --> 00:33:11.163 position:19% line:83% align:start
What's there to teach?
Just do it!

00:33:11.196 --> 00:33:11.863 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
I can't.

00:33:11.897 --> 00:33:12.531 position:41% line:89% align:start
Do it!

00:33:12.564 --> 00:33:13.031 position:38% line:89% align:start
I can't.

00:33:13.065 --> 00:33:14.866 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ah! Stubborn boy!

00:33:14.900 --> 00:33:16.268 position:30% line:83% align:start
Find a way to
explain it to him.

00:33:16.301 --> 00:33:17.302 position:13% line:89% align:start
Try using different words.

00:33:17.336 --> 00:33:18.437 position:13% line:89% align:start
Fine. I'll think of some,

00:33:18.470 --> 00:33:21.540 position:10% line:83% align:start
but I don't see what's wrong
with the ones I used.

00:33:21.573 --> 00:33:24.075 position:16% line:83% align:start
You need to grab hold of
the sword that's in here.

00:33:24.108 --> 00:33:26.311 position:30% line:83% align:start
In your soul.
You have one, don't you?

00:33:26.345 --> 00:33:28.212 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
What? You don't make any sense.

00:33:28.245 --> 00:33:31.215 position:16% line:83% align:start
How much clearer do you
need me to make it for you?

00:33:31.248 --> 00:33:34.185 position:24% line:83% align:start
You grab the sword
that's in your soul.

00:33:34.218 --> 00:33:37.388 position:24% line:89% align:start
Okay. Now, do it.

00:33:37.421 --> 00:33:39.090 position:41% line:89% align:start
Do it!

00:33:45.296 --> 00:33:46.364 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hmph.

00:33:46.397 --> 00:33:48.932 position:5% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Hey, wait a minute,
where are you going?

00:33:48.965 --> 00:33:51.067 position:35% line:83% align:start
Come now.
Yelling and walking off?

00:33:51.101 --> 00:33:53.371 position:5% line:89% align:start
Not the best teaching technique.

00:33:53.404 --> 00:33:56.039 position:35% line:83% align:start
Kumatetsu.
Come back, Kumatetsu.

00:33:56.072 --> 00:33:56.973 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Hmph.

00:33:57.006 --> 00:34:00.210 position:5% line:89% align:start
A sword in my soul? That's dumb.

00:34:00.243 --> 00:34:02.612 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Hey, kid. Just go home.

00:34:02.645 --> 00:34:03.781 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:34:03.814 --> 00:34:06.349 position:10% line:83% align:start
Apprentices train for five,
even ten years sometimes.

00:34:06.383 --> 00:34:09.285 position:10% line:83% align:start
You'll never make it, I mean
even you must realize that.

00:34:09.319 --> 00:34:10.620 position:16% line:89% align:start
Quit wasting your time.

00:34:10.653 --> 00:34:13.256 position:27% line:83% align:start
Go find a human
to take care of you.

00:34:13.289 --> 00:34:15.124 position:7% line:89% align:start
There's no place for you here.

00:34:15.157 --> 00:34:18.060 position:16% line:83% align:start
Do yourself a favor and
go back to your world.

00:34:18.628 --> 00:34:21.930 position:21% line:89% align:start
[chickens clucking]

00:34:21.964 --> 00:34:24.133 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where'd he go?

00:34:24.166 --> 00:34:25.334 position:38% line:89% align:start
He left.

00:34:25.367 --> 00:34:28.337 position:10% line:83% align:start
He said we shouldn't expect
to see him for a few days.

00:34:28.370 --> 00:34:32.274 position:30% line:83% align:start
What do I do?
As his apprentice, I mean.

00:34:32.307 --> 00:34:34.976 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Well, you clean
the house, and do the laundry,

00:34:35.009 --> 00:34:36.345 position:27% line:89% align:start
and the cooking.

00:34:36.378 --> 00:34:39.180 position:19% line:83% align:start
So eager to help now.
Is this about yesterday?

00:34:39.213 --> 00:34:40.516 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
No, not really.

00:34:40.549 --> 00:34:43.084 position:21% line:89% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO coughs]

00:34:43.117 --> 00:34:44.085 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't mind him.

00:34:44.118 --> 00:34:46.588 position:27% line:83% align:start
He has a temper.
Nobody is going to deny that.

00:34:46.622 --> 00:34:48.956 position:10% line:83% align:start
But the nice thing about him
is he forgets everything

00:34:48.990 --> 00:34:49.957 position:30% line:89% align:start
the next day.

00:34:49.991 --> 00:34:52.427 position:16% line:83% align:start
I really wouldn't let it
concern you too much.

00:34:52.460 --> 00:34:54.328 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
It isn't about yesterday.

00:34:54.362 --> 00:34:56.397 position:24% line:83% align:start
They'll wrinkle if
you do it like that.

00:34:56.431 --> 00:34:58.666 position:19% line:83% align:start
You want to give them
a good shake first.

00:34:58.699 --> 00:35:01.067 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Oh.

00:35:01.101 --> 00:35:02.437 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Hmm.

00:35:11.144 --> 00:35:13.513 position:7% line:83% align:start
[MALE CLERK BEAST] I've never
had a human customer before.

00:35:13.547 --> 00:35:14.581 position:24% line:89% align:start
Really? Not ever?

00:35:14.614 --> 00:35:16.483 position:5% line:89% align:start
How long are you staying, then?

00:35:16.516 --> 00:35:17.684 position:30% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:35:17.717 --> 00:35:19.986 position:27% line:83% align:start
He's not a very
polite young man.

00:35:20.020 --> 00:35:24.023 position:7% line:83% align:start
Bah! Humans are all hopeless.
Everyone knows that.

00:35:24.056 --> 00:35:26.293 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO grunts]

00:35:26.326 --> 00:35:27.993 position:24% line:89% align:start
[GIRL BEASTS sigh]

00:35:28.027 --> 00:35:28.662 position:35% line:89% align:start
[applause]

00:35:28.695 --> 00:35:30.530 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO sighs]

00:35:30.564 --> 00:35:34.534 position:7% line:89% align:start
[GIRL BEASTS chatter, giggle]

00:35:34.568 --> 00:35:35.535 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Huh?

00:35:35.569 --> 00:35:37.503 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
Human! Monster!

00:35:37.536 --> 00:35:38.471 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

00:35:38.504 --> 00:35:40.573 position:21% line:83% align:start
I heard what my dad
said about you people.

00:35:40.606 --> 00:35:44.376 position:16% line:83% align:start
Humans are bad. Someday,
they become monsters!

00:35:44.410 --> 00:35:46.645 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, I'm not gonna wait.
I'll hunt you down now!

00:35:46.679 --> 00:35:49.482 position:7% line:89% align:start
Stop it. Just leave him alone.

00:35:49.515 --> 00:35:50.449 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why should I?

00:35:50.483 --> 00:35:52.050 position:7% line:89% align:start
You see what a weakling he is.

00:35:52.083 --> 00:35:54.018 position:7% line:89% align:start
He'll never become a monster.

00:35:54.052 --> 00:35:56.589 position:7% line:83% align:start
I think I can keep my brother
from attacking you again.

00:35:56.622 --> 00:35:58.022 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll try, at least.

00:35:58.056 --> 00:35:59.090 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
You better not tell on me.

00:35:59.123 --> 00:36:00.258 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll know if you do!

00:36:00.291 --> 00:36:01.794 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
That's enough. Let's go.

00:36:01.827 --> 00:36:03.661 position:7% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU] I don't like wimps.
They're losers.

00:36:03.696 --> 00:36:05.497 position:27% line:83% align:start
Everybody should
know how to fight.

00:36:05.530 --> 00:36:08.366 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey! Do you even know how
strong my brother is, human?

00:36:08.399 --> 00:36:10.635 position:24% line:83% align:start
He can move things
without touching them!

00:36:10.668 --> 00:36:12.437 position:7% line:89% align:start
Show the wimp what you can do!

00:36:12.470 --> 00:36:13.371 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:36:13.404 --> 00:36:15.406 position:24% line:83% align:start
You know my power
isn't for showing off.

00:36:15.440 --> 00:36:19.444 position:5% line:83% align:start
Father says that I should always
try to use it to help people.

00:36:19.477 --> 00:36:21.211 position:7% line:89% align:start
And I do what Father tells me.

00:36:21.245 --> 00:36:23.781 position:16% line:83% align:start
Because if I do, I know
I'll be like him someday.

00:36:23.815 --> 00:36:24.616 position:24% line:89% align:start
A great swordsman.

00:36:24.649 --> 00:36:27.217 position:27% line:83% align:start
One with a long
snout and big fangs!

00:36:27.251 --> 00:36:28.385 position:38% line:89% align:start
Me, too!

00:36:28.418 --> 00:36:31.188 position:13% line:83% align:start
When I grow up, I'm gonna
be a good fighter like Dad!

00:36:31.221 --> 00:36:32.089 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Let's go.

00:36:32.122 --> 00:36:33.056 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
'Kay!

00:36:33.090 --> 00:36:34.658 position:10% line:89% align:start
[BOY BEASTS laugh, chatter]

00:36:34.691 --> 00:36:36.560 position:19% line:89% align:start
[GIRL BEASTS giggles]

00:36:36.593 --> 00:36:38.462 position:7% line:89% align:start
He thinks I'm just a weakling.

00:36:38.495 --> 00:36:41.798 position:21% line:89% align:start
Well... he's wrong.

00:36:41.832 --> 00:36:43.700 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU sighs]

00:36:43.734 --> 00:36:45.402 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:36:45.435 --> 00:36:46.402 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, what happened?!

00:36:46.436 --> 00:36:48.705 position:19% line:83% align:start
Where's all my stuff?!
Who cleaned up in here?!

00:36:48.739 --> 00:36:50.406 position:24% line:83% align:start
Who do you think?
Your apprentice.

00:36:50.439 --> 00:36:52.809 position:21% line:83% align:start
I liked it just fine
the way it was!

00:36:52.843 --> 00:36:54.677 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:36:54.710 --> 00:36:57.146 position:10% line:89% align:start
What happened to your face?

00:36:57.179 --> 00:36:59.348 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Heh. You got beat up, huh?

00:36:59.382 --> 00:37:01.784 position:19% line:83% align:start
I bet you didn't even
put up a decent fight.

00:37:01.817 --> 00:37:03.452 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ha! Pathetic.

00:37:03.486 --> 00:37:05.221 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're right.
I'm weak and pathetic.

00:37:05.254 --> 00:37:07.290 position:7% line:89% align:start
I can't fight or hold a sword.

00:37:07.323 --> 00:37:08.624 position:24% line:89% align:start
At least you know.

00:37:08.658 --> 00:37:09.692 position:16% line:89% align:start
Try looking in a mirror.

00:37:09.725 --> 00:37:12.160 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm not the only one
around here who's pathetic.

00:37:12.193 --> 00:37:13.295 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:37:13.328 --> 00:37:15.698 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] He wakes up early.
You stay in bed till noon.

00:37:15.731 --> 00:37:18.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's busy all day
doing useful stuff.

00:37:18.433 --> 00:37:20.468 position:30% line:83% align:start
You don't ever
seem to do anything!

00:37:20.502 --> 00:37:23.104 position:16% line:83% align:start
I assume the "he" you're
talking about is Iozen?

00:37:23.138 --> 00:37:25.373 position:19% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] He seems tidy,
polite, and dependable.

00:37:25.407 --> 00:37:27.842 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're sloppy, rude,
and irresponsible.

00:37:27.876 --> 00:37:29.377 position:16% line:89% align:start
And your point would be?

00:37:29.411 --> 00:37:31.546 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] Just that it makes
total sense to me now

00:37:31.580 --> 00:37:34.181 position:16% line:89% align:start
that you can't beat him.

00:37:34.214 --> 00:37:36.585 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Say it again, brat!

00:37:36.618 --> 00:37:38.653 position:21% line:89% align:start
Go on! Say it again!

00:37:38.687 --> 00:37:40.220 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
I'll say it a hundred times!

00:37:40.254 --> 00:37:41.856 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're a big, stupid loser!

00:37:41.890 --> 00:37:43.424 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Calm down, both of you.

00:37:43.457 --> 00:37:45.459 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] Don't talk to
your master like that!

00:37:45.492 --> 00:37:47.595 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] Then start acting
more like a master!

00:37:47.628 --> 00:37:48.462 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
What?!

00:37:48.495 --> 00:37:49.363 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
You heard me!

00:37:49.396 --> 00:37:50.864 position:13% line:89% align:start
You get angry too easily!

00:37:50.898 --> 00:37:51.699 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hey!

00:37:51.732 --> 00:37:53.667 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
And you give up too easily!

00:37:53.701 --> 00:37:55.803 position:21% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] It's not
your place to criticize me!

00:37:55.836 --> 00:37:58.338 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're my apprentice.
You have to do what I say!

00:37:58.371 --> 00:37:59.440 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Never!

00:37:59.473 --> 00:38:01.609 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't want to end up a stupid,
old loser like you!

00:38:01.642 --> 00:38:03.176 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
You're a little brat!

00:38:03.209 --> 00:38:04.611 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Well, you're a big idiot!

00:38:04.645 --> 00:38:05.846 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Try to forgive him, Kyuta.

00:38:05.879 --> 00:38:07.680 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's new to this,
just like you are.

00:38:07.714 --> 00:38:10.183 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Come on, Kumatetsu,
let's take a walk.

00:38:10.216 --> 00:38:12.819 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Let go! Let go!

00:38:12.852 --> 00:38:15.188 position:24% line:89% align:start
Brat! Brat! Brat!

00:38:15.221 --> 00:38:17.690 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm doing the best I can,
and what do I get?!

00:38:17.724 --> 00:38:19.626 position:5% line:89% align:start
He doesn't show me any respect!

00:38:19.659 --> 00:38:20.893 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
You've done enough.

00:38:20.927 --> 00:38:21.861 position:10% line:89% align:start
Just kick him out, already.

00:38:21.894 --> 00:38:23.930 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
I do useful things, you know!

00:38:23.963 --> 00:38:26.431 position:27% line:83% align:start
I chop wood and
take care of the chickens.

00:38:26.465 --> 00:38:27.532 position:30% line:89% align:start
I do odd jobs.

00:38:27.566 --> 00:38:29.401 position:5% line:89% align:start
What more does he want from me?!

00:38:29.434 --> 00:38:31.737 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] I'm telling you,
it's time to end this.

00:38:31.771 --> 00:38:33.840 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] He has no right
to talk to me like that!

00:38:33.873 --> 00:38:36.308 position:19% line:83% align:start
You agree, don't you?
Well, don't you?!

00:38:36.341 --> 00:38:37.309 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, absolutely.

00:38:37.342 --> 00:38:39.945 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now don't you see how
easy it was being alone?

00:38:39.978 --> 00:38:41.480 position:19% line:89% align:start
Being alone is great!

00:38:41.513 --> 00:38:42.648 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's no responsibility,

00:38:42.681 --> 00:38:45.751 position:13% line:83% align:start
you don't have to justify
your actions to anyone else,

00:38:45.784 --> 00:38:47.284 position:24% line:83% align:start
you don't have to
hear hard truths

00:38:47.318 --> 00:38:48.620 position:7% line:89% align:start
that will just make you angry.

00:38:48.654 --> 00:38:49.320 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:38:49.353 --> 00:38:51.255 position:5% line:89% align:start
Uh, forget that last one, okay?

00:38:51.288 --> 00:38:52.824 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Arrrgh!

00:38:52.858 --> 00:38:54.425 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Training so late into the night?

00:38:54.458 --> 00:38:57.294 position:13% line:83% align:start
What incredible dedication
you have, Kumatetsu.

00:38:57.328 --> 00:38:58.596 position:35% line:89% align:start
Lord, I--

00:38:58.629 --> 00:39:00.831 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's good for a master
to show his apprentice

00:39:00.865 --> 00:39:02.266 position:13% line:89% align:start
that training never stops,

00:39:02.299 --> 00:39:04.402 position:30% line:83% align:start
no matter your
age or experience.

00:39:04.435 --> 00:39:06.604 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Uh, right. My thoughts exactly.

00:39:06.637 --> 00:39:09.707 position:10% line:83% align:start
Here. You can take these as
a reward for your efforts.

00:39:09.740 --> 00:39:10.508 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
What are they?

00:39:10.541 --> 00:39:12.308 position:16% line:89% align:start
Letters of introduction.

00:39:12.342 --> 00:39:13.176 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
What for?

00:39:13.209 --> 00:39:14.645 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
You'll be taking your apprentice

00:39:14.679 --> 00:39:16.279 position:10% line:89% align:start
on an instructional journey.

00:39:16.312 --> 00:39:17.715 position:7% line:89% align:start
If you present those letters,

00:39:17.748 --> 00:39:20.483 position:16% line:83% align:start
you will be able to meet
the lord of every land.

00:39:20.517 --> 00:39:21.284 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
But I--

00:39:21.317 --> 00:39:22.987 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
They're all very wise men.

00:39:23.020 --> 00:39:24.688 position:24% line:83% align:start
They will be able
to give you insight

00:39:24.721 --> 00:39:26.690 position:21% line:83% align:start
regarding the nature
of true strength.

00:39:26.723 --> 00:39:27.857 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
But, sir...

00:39:27.891 --> 00:39:29.392 position:33% line:89% align:start
[BOTH gasp]

00:39:29.426 --> 00:39:32.629 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Bon voyage! Safe travels!

00:39:32.662 --> 00:39:33.730 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TATARA groans]

00:39:33.763 --> 00:39:36.599 position:5% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] There goes your chance
to kick the kid out.

00:39:36.633 --> 00:39:37.967 position:24% line:83% align:start
If you do it now,
you'll be disobeying

00:39:38.001 --> 00:39:40.870 position:5% line:89% align:start
the lord's direct instructions.

00:39:49.912 --> 00:39:51.380 position:16% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU] Too slow.
--[KYUTA grunts]

00:39:51.413 --> 00:39:52.748 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:39:54.850 --> 00:39:56.719 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA pants]

00:39:56.752 --> 00:39:58.287 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Too slow.

00:40:11.666 --> 00:40:13.801 position:10% line:89% align:start
Too slow! Slow, slow, slow!

00:40:13.835 --> 00:40:15.503 position:41% line:89% align:start
Geez!

00:40:15.536 --> 00:40:17.805 position:19% line:83% align:start
There's nothing wrong
with eating slowly.

00:40:19.073 --> 00:40:21.375 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
We humbly seek your counsel.

00:40:21.409 --> 00:40:22.944 position:19% line:89% align:start
What is true strength?

00:40:22.977 --> 00:40:25.046 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KOKURAN DOJIN] I don't have
the powerful muscles

00:40:25.079 --> 00:40:26.681 position:19% line:89% align:start
that many fighters do.

00:40:26.714 --> 00:40:30.618 position:7% line:83% align:start
However, I do have the ability
to create illusions.

00:40:30.651 --> 00:40:33.755 position:13% line:83% align:start
And sometimes there can be
more truth within an illusion

00:40:33.788 --> 00:40:34.922 position:27% line:89% align:start
than in reality.

00:40:34.956 --> 00:40:36.590 position:7% line:89% align:start
Therefore, true strength is...

00:40:36.623 --> 00:40:37.891 position:21% line:89% align:start
True strength is...?

00:40:37.925 --> 00:40:39.392 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ALL gasp]

00:40:39.426 --> 00:40:41.461 position:27% line:83% align:start
[KOKURAN DOJIN]
Why, it's an illusion!

00:40:41.495 --> 00:40:42.529 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:40:42.562 --> 00:40:43.363 position:44% line:89% align:start
Tch!

00:40:43.396 --> 00:40:44.232 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
What is true strength?

00:40:44.264 --> 00:40:45.899 position:30% line:83% align:start
[SHAKO INSHI]
What good is strength?

00:40:45.932 --> 00:40:47.701 position:7% line:89% align:start
That's what I'd like to know.

00:40:47.734 --> 00:40:49.836 position:21% line:83% align:start
I possess the power
of telekinesis,

00:40:49.870 --> 00:40:51.538 position:21% line:83% align:start
which may seem like
strength to you.

00:40:51.571 --> 00:40:54.573 position:10% line:83% align:start
But there is something even
my ability is powerless against.

00:40:54.608 --> 00:40:55.976 position:7% line:89% align:start
Therefore, true strength is...

00:40:56.009 --> 00:40:57.844 position:21% line:89% align:start
True strength is...?

00:40:57.878 --> 00:40:59.913 position:30% line:83% align:start
[SHAKO INSHI]
Could you do me a favor?

00:40:59.946 --> 00:41:02.681 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's my back. I really could
use a good massage.

00:41:02.715 --> 00:41:05.818 position:19% line:83% align:start
Telekinesis does squat
for lower back pain.

00:41:05.851 --> 00:41:06.919 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:41:06.952 --> 00:41:07.987 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:41:08.020 --> 00:41:09.121 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ZABO SENSEI]
Strength?

00:41:09.155 --> 00:41:11.957 position:7% line:83% align:start
I fear you've come a long way
to ask the wrong person.

00:41:11.991 --> 00:41:14.894 position:13% line:83% align:start
I do not try to be strong.
I try to simply be.

00:41:14.927 --> 00:41:17.930 position:13% line:83% align:start
Rain or shine, I sit here
like any other rock.

00:41:17.963 --> 00:41:18.998 position:33% line:89% align:start
Why a rock?

00:41:19.031 --> 00:41:21.767 position:19% line:83% align:start
To forget about time,
and the world, and myself.

00:41:21.801 --> 00:41:25.403 position:5% line:83% align:start
Only by doing so can I transcend
the confines of reality.

00:41:25.436 --> 00:41:26.471 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thus, true strength is...

00:41:26.504 --> 00:41:28.673 position:21% line:89% align:start
True strength is...?

00:41:28.706 --> 00:41:30.775 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:41:30.809 --> 00:41:32.844 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Still and silent, like a rock.

00:41:32.877 --> 00:41:34.012 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:41:34.045 --> 00:41:35.380 position:27% line:83% align:start
[KYUZEN NENSHI]
True strength?

00:41:35.413 --> 00:41:37.782 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't like to get
philosophical.

00:41:37.816 --> 00:41:40.985 position:16% line:83% align:start
The key to fishing is to
strike when the time is right.

00:41:41.019 --> 00:41:42.452 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ahhh...

00:41:44.588 --> 00:41:46.024 position:24% line:83% align:start
The fishermen who
wait for their opening

00:41:46.057 --> 00:41:48.692 position:5% line:83% align:start
and act at the opportune moment
catch the most fish.

00:41:48.725 --> 00:41:49.928 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gulps]

00:41:49.961 --> 00:41:52.596 position:5% line:83% align:start
--Therefore, true strength is...
--Yes, true strength is...?

00:41:52.629 --> 00:41:53.730 position:24% line:89% align:start
All in the timing!

00:41:53.764 --> 00:41:54.731 position:21% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO, KYUTA]
Ah!

00:41:54.765 --> 00:41:59.369 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TATARA yells]

00:42:01.705 --> 00:42:03.473 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't worry. I avoid
eating my guests.

00:42:03.507 --> 00:42:06.910 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yawns]

00:42:06.944 --> 00:42:08.679 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] Are we actually
supposed to learn something

00:42:08.712 --> 00:42:10.147 position:7% line:89% align:start
by listening to this nonsense?

00:42:10.180 --> 00:42:12.548 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] I learned that almost
being eaten isn't fun.

00:42:12.582 --> 00:42:13.749 position:27% line:89% align:start
Does that count?

00:42:13.783 --> 00:42:15.618 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] The point is that
strength can be a lot of things.

00:42:15.651 --> 00:42:17.553 position:19% line:83% align:start
I thought they all had
interesting stuff to say.

00:42:17.587 --> 00:42:19.388 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Ooh! Maybe you'd be better off

00:42:19.422 --> 00:42:20.857 position:10% line:89% align:start
holding a book than a sword!

00:42:20.890 --> 00:42:22.091 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Maybe I would!

00:42:22.124 --> 00:42:24.493 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm sure I'd learn a lot more
from reading than from you.

00:42:24.527 --> 00:42:27.563 position:10% line:83% align:start
At least a book will tell me
more than "woosh" and "bam."

00:42:27.597 --> 00:42:29.565 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] Some things you
gotta figure out on your own!

00:42:29.599 --> 00:42:30.900 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Because you can't explain it!

00:42:30.933 --> 00:42:32.567 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Because you're too stupid!

00:42:32.602 --> 00:42:34.402 position:19% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] Because you're
terrible at teaching!

00:42:34.436 --> 00:42:35.338 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Because you're terrible...

00:42:35.370 --> 00:42:36.873 position:19% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] No matter
how tired you are,

00:42:36.906 --> 00:42:38.908 position:16% line:83% align:start
you two can always find
the energy to argue.

00:42:38.941 --> 00:42:41.476 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Just listening to
you guys is exhausting me.

00:42:41.509 --> 00:42:42.844 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Hey!

00:42:54.556 --> 00:42:56.925 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Having trouble
sleeping, are you?

00:42:56.958 --> 00:42:59.526 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you think I'm just
wasting my time with all this?

00:42:59.560 --> 00:43:01.029 position:7% line:89% align:start
You're letting him get to you.

00:43:01.062 --> 00:43:02.630 position:16% line:89% align:start
He says that I'm stupid.

00:43:02.663 --> 00:43:04.933 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, I can tell you
that isn't true.

00:43:04.966 --> 00:43:06.667 position:24% line:83% align:start
Just look at what
you've done so far.

00:43:06.700 --> 00:43:08.469 position:16% line:83% align:start
You didn't know anything
about housework,

00:43:08.502 --> 00:43:10.104 position:19% line:83% align:start
but you got the knack
of it right away.

00:43:10.138 --> 00:43:12.072 position:24% line:83% align:start
You work hard and
you learn quickly.

00:43:12.106 --> 00:43:13.707 position:5% line:89% align:start
I think you're far from stupid.

00:43:13.741 --> 00:43:15.910 position:30% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:43:15.943 --> 00:43:18.545 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] The problem in
this case lies with Kumatetsu.

00:43:18.579 --> 00:43:20.581 position:16% line:83% align:start
His fighting techniques
are like him.

00:43:20.614 --> 00:43:23.449 position:21% line:83% align:start
A little bit rough.
Definitely on the messy side.

00:43:23.483 --> 00:43:25.585 position:33% line:89% align:start
But strong.

00:43:25.618 --> 00:43:28.521 position:24% line:83% align:start
He had no parents
or master to teach him.

00:43:28.554 --> 00:43:29.522 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Huh?

00:43:29.555 --> 00:43:32.059 position:16% line:83% align:start
He had to become strong
without anybody's help.

00:43:32.092 --> 00:43:34.027 position:30% line:83% align:start
In some ways,
that's his greatest asset.

00:43:34.060 --> 00:43:37.030 position:21% line:83% align:start
In others, however,
it's his greatest failing.

00:43:37.063 --> 00:43:39.098 position:24% line:83% align:start
Because he learned
everything independently,

00:43:39.132 --> 00:43:41.668 position:16% line:83% align:start
he can now neither take
instruction nor give it.

00:43:41.701 --> 00:43:43.603 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can see how
that would happen.

00:43:43.636 --> 00:43:44.704 position:24% line:89% align:start
Despite all that,

00:43:44.737 --> 00:43:47.740 position:10% line:83% align:start
he's still capable of wisdom
every once in a while.

00:43:47.774 --> 00:43:49.976 position:13% line:89% align:start
Like what he said earlier.

00:43:50.009 --> 00:43:51.510 position:24% line:83% align:start
When he said there
are some things

00:43:51.543 --> 00:43:53.112 position:5% line:89% align:start
I have to figure out on my own?

00:43:53.146 --> 00:43:57.083 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Yes. I believe
there was some truth to that.

00:44:00.652 --> 00:44:02.087 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
I don't know how to teach him.

00:44:02.120 --> 00:44:03.188 position:30% line:89% align:start
I just don't.

00:44:03.221 --> 00:44:05.490 position:16% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] I never thought
I'd hear the great Kumatetsu

00:44:05.524 --> 00:44:07.526 position:27% line:83% align:start
crying over some
cocky little kid.

00:44:07.559 --> 00:44:09.227 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, I'm not crying.

00:44:09.261 --> 00:44:11.129 position:19% line:83% align:start
You were just like him
when you were younger.

00:44:11.163 --> 00:44:13.098 position:24% line:83% align:start
A weak little kid
with a big mouth.

00:44:13.131 --> 00:44:15.867 position:10% line:83% align:start
You thought you already knew
everything there was to know.

00:44:15.901 --> 00:44:18.270 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] There weren't
any decent masters.

00:44:18.303 --> 00:44:20.638 position:16% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Nobody thought
you were worth anything.

00:44:20.671 --> 00:44:22.240 position:27% line:89% align:start
Except the lord.

00:44:22.274 --> 00:44:24.642 position:19% line:83% align:start
They all looked at you
and saw a difficult student

00:44:24.675 --> 00:44:26.077 position:21% line:83% align:start
they didn't want to
waste their time on.

00:44:26.110 --> 00:44:27.312 position:41% line:89% align:start
Fools!

00:44:27.346 --> 00:44:29.680 position:10% line:83% align:start
Just thinking about them is
still enough to make me mad.

00:44:29.714 --> 00:44:30.982 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Funny you say that.

00:44:31.015 --> 00:44:32.750 position:24% line:83% align:start
Because you're in
their shoes now.

00:44:32.783 --> 00:44:34.018 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Huh?

00:44:34.051 --> 00:44:36.754 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well. Personally, I still think
it would be best for everybody

00:44:36.787 --> 00:44:37.955 position:27% line:89% align:start
