00:44:37.989 --> 00:44:40.824 position:7% line:83% align:start
If you really want to continue
with this idiocy, though.

00:44:40.858 --> 00:44:42.759 position:7% line:89% align:start
Remember how you started out.

00:44:42.792 --> 00:44:45.029 position:24% line:83% align:start
Try thinking about
yourself as a kid.

00:44:45.062 --> 00:44:46.997 position:24% line:83% align:start
It might help you
understand him better.

00:44:47.030 --> 00:44:49.766 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TATARA yawns]

00:44:49.799 --> 00:44:51.935 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
And I'm going to sleep.

00:44:54.637 --> 00:44:56.006 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

00:45:00.143 --> 00:45:04.713 position:19% line:83% align:start
I just have to figure
it out on my own, huh?

00:45:04.747 --> 00:45:06.149 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:45:06.182 --> 00:45:08.051 position:16% line:89% align:start
And how does that work?

00:45:10.753 --> 00:45:11.720 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:45:11.754 --> 00:45:15.657 position:33% line:89% align:start
[squeaking]

00:45:15.691 --> 00:45:17.559 position:30% line:89% align:start
Eep, eep, eep!

00:45:17.593 --> 00:45:19.094 position:7% line:89% align:start
I think that was pretty good.

00:45:19.128 --> 00:45:20.162 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaks]

00:45:20.195 --> 00:45:22.064 position:33% line:89% align:start
No? Really?

00:45:22.097 --> 00:45:26.201 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:45:26.235 --> 00:45:29.271 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S MOTHER]
Be your master. Do as he does.

00:45:34.942 --> 00:45:37.312 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, Chico, you hear that?

00:45:39.281 --> 00:45:41.883 position:27% line:89% align:start
Be your master.

00:45:41.916 --> 00:45:45.119 position:24% line:89% align:start
Be your master...

00:45:45.153 --> 00:45:48.222 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:45:48.256 --> 00:45:49.791 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU groans]

00:45:51.993 --> 00:45:53.094 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yawns]

00:45:53.127 --> 00:45:56.064 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gasps, yawns]

00:45:56.097 --> 00:45:56.797 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hm?!

00:45:56.830 --> 00:45:58.166 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:46:07.841 --> 00:46:09.743 position:19% line:89% align:start
Do as he does. Right.

00:46:09.776 --> 00:46:14.848 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunting]

00:46:16.049 --> 00:46:17.683 position:33% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU]

00:46:17.716 --> 00:46:19.785 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's what I need to be doing.

00:46:26.426 --> 00:46:27.960 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:46:36.435 --> 00:46:38.671 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunting]

00:46:38.704 --> 00:46:41.706 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunting]

00:46:41.739 --> 00:46:42.942 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA yelps, yells]

00:46:42.975 --> 00:46:43.775 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hm?!

00:46:43.808 --> 00:46:44.609 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:46:44.642 --> 00:46:47.246 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kyuta. What are you
up to in here?

00:46:48.347 --> 00:46:51.749 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S MOTHER]
Be your master. Do as he does.

00:46:54.353 --> 00:46:55.887 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:46:55.920 --> 00:46:56.988 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU sniffs]

00:46:57.021 --> 00:46:58.156 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA sniffs]

00:46:58.189 --> 00:46:59.724 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:47:02.160 --> 00:47:04.095 position:24% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts,
bones crack]

00:47:04.129 --> 00:47:05.897 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA grunts,
bones crack]

00:47:19.309 --> 00:47:21.078 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Now what are they doing?

00:47:21.111 --> 00:47:22.713 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you making fun of me?!

00:47:22.746 --> 00:47:23.780 position:33% line:89% align:start
No! I'm not!

00:47:23.814 --> 00:47:24.982 position:21% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?!

00:47:25.015 --> 00:47:26.250 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's nothing, okay?

00:47:26.283 --> 00:47:27.818 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hmph!

00:47:35.925 --> 00:47:38.027 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
You're driving me nuts!

00:47:44.867 --> 00:47:45.902 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Where...?

00:47:45.935 --> 00:47:47.370 position:7% line:89% align:start
Geez. What is that kid up to?

00:47:47.403 --> 00:47:49.472 position:10% line:83% align:start
Learning. He's the duckling.
You're the duck.

00:47:49.505 --> 00:47:50.673 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm not a duck, thank you.

00:47:50.706 --> 00:47:53.976 position:10% line:83% align:start
How else does a child learn
but by imitating his father?

00:47:54.010 --> 00:47:55.777 position:16% line:89% align:start
Not his father, either.

00:47:55.810 --> 00:47:56.979 position:38% line:89% align:start
Listen.

00:47:57.013 --> 00:47:58.880 position:7% line:83% align:start
He's trying to learn from you
the most basic way he can.

00:47:58.914 --> 00:48:01.117 position:21% line:83% align:start
The same way a baby
learns from his father.

00:48:01.150 --> 00:48:03.018 position:33% line:89% align:start
A baby, huh?

00:48:06.922 --> 00:48:08.256 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hmph.

00:48:17.866 --> 00:48:19.034 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:48:19.067 --> 00:48:20.202 position:24% line:89% align:start
Look at Kumatetsu.

00:48:20.235 --> 00:48:22.103 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think he's actually
enjoying this.

00:48:22.137 --> 00:48:24.206 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, every father
in the world enjoys it

00:48:24.239 --> 00:48:25.407 position:13% line:89% align:start
when his son imitates him.

00:48:25.440 --> 00:48:26.840 position:33% line:89% align:start
Doesn't he?

00:48:26.874 --> 00:48:27.775 position:27% line:89% align:start
All right, kid.

00:48:27.808 --> 00:48:29.843 position:19% line:83% align:start
How long are you gonna
keep this up for?

00:48:29.877 --> 00:48:32.480 position:7% line:83% align:start
Being a copycat isn't going to
make you a good swordsman.

00:48:32.514 --> 00:48:34.449 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Hey! We're working, here.

00:48:34.482 --> 00:48:35.517 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:48:35.550 --> 00:48:37.985 position:16% line:83% align:start
Earlier you said he was
driving you nuts, though.

00:48:38.018 --> 00:48:39.920 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Just go away, would ya?

00:48:39.954 --> 00:48:42.423 position:7% line:83% align:start
Well, he's definitely changed
his tune, hasn't he?

00:48:42.456 --> 00:48:43.324 position:19% line:89% align:start
When did that happen?

00:48:43.357 --> 00:48:44.425 position:30% line:89% align:start
Strange, huh?

00:48:44.458 --> 00:48:46.927 position:16% line:83% align:start
He must have developed a
fondness for his apprentice.

00:48:46.961 --> 00:48:49.796 position:33% line:83% align:start
Hah! No way.
That would never happen to--

00:48:51.831 --> 00:48:53.200 position:33% line:89% align:start
Seriously?!

00:49:14.254 --> 00:49:15.854 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Oh, yeah? I'll show you!

00:49:15.887 --> 00:49:16.922 position:24% line:89% align:start
How you like this?

00:49:16.955 --> 00:49:18.358 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ha! That works for me!

00:49:18.391 --> 00:49:19.958 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TATARA gasps]
I want to take it back!

00:49:19.992 --> 00:49:20.693 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Too late!

00:49:20.727 --> 00:49:22.327 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Aw, come on! Come on!

00:49:22.361 --> 00:49:23.463 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Mwah!

00:49:23.496 --> 00:49:24.796 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Please? This isn't fair!

00:49:24.830 --> 00:49:26.365 position:27% line:83% align:start
I didn't mean to
discard that one!

00:49:26.398 --> 00:49:29.468 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU laughs]

00:49:37.242 --> 00:49:38.776 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

00:49:45.249 --> 00:49:47.018 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm not watching...

00:49:50.187 --> 00:49:51.822 position:30% line:89% align:start
I can't see...

00:49:53.424 --> 00:49:55.493 position:30% line:89% align:start
But I know...

00:49:55.526 --> 00:50:01.332 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[TATARA growls]
--[KUMATETSU laughs]

00:50:01.365 --> 00:50:02.466 position:33% line:89% align:start
Time to try.

00:50:02.500 --> 00:50:07.505 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:50:07.538 --> 00:50:10.206 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Hm?

00:50:10.240 --> 00:50:13.276 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Ow! Ow!

00:50:13.310 --> 00:50:15.011 position:16% line:89% align:start
What's gotten into him?

00:50:15.045 --> 00:50:17.914 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey! Stupid kid! Stop it!

00:50:17.947 --> 00:50:20.050 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh...?

00:50:20.083 --> 00:50:21.418 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

00:50:23.086 --> 00:50:24.521 position:16% line:89% align:start
He can't possibly be...

00:50:24.554 --> 00:50:26.423 position:19% line:89% align:start
Kyuta, how are you...?

00:50:26.456 --> 00:50:28.625 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] I spent so long
watching and copying his steps,

00:50:28.658 --> 00:50:30.959 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can guess what
he's gonna do next.

00:50:30.993 --> 00:50:33.062 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
What?! No way!

00:50:33.095 --> 00:50:34.564 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yells]

00:50:34.597 --> 00:50:35.398 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:50:35.432 --> 00:50:37.900 position:21% line:83% align:start
You kicked his butt!
Good job, Kyuta!

00:50:37.933 --> 00:50:41.003 position:10% line:83% align:start
Maybe you aren't as hopeless
as I thought you were!

00:50:41.036 --> 00:50:44.173 position:7% line:83% align:start
Looks like you'll be learning
from him now, Kumatetsu.

00:50:44.206 --> 00:50:46.175 position:27% line:89% align:start
Learn from him?

00:50:46.208 --> 00:50:47.576 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're joking, right?!

00:50:47.609 --> 00:50:48.644 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
I don't mind teaching you.

00:50:48.677 --> 00:50:49.545 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:50:49.578 --> 00:50:51.046 position:30% line:89% align:start
In exchange...

00:50:51.080 --> 00:50:52.247 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Exchange?

00:50:52.281 --> 00:50:55.149 position:13% line:83% align:start
I still don't know how to
hold a sword or throw a punch.

00:50:55.184 --> 00:50:57.586 position:7% line:89% align:start
I can't figure that out alone.

00:50:57.619 --> 00:50:59.621 position:13% line:89% align:start
Will you please teach me?

00:51:07.161 --> 00:51:08.429 position:27% line:83% align:start
--[KYUTA yelps]
--[CHICO squeaks]

00:51:08.463 --> 00:51:10.264 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

00:51:10.298 --> 00:51:11.466 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:51:11.499 --> 00:51:13.468 position:7% line:89% align:start
Now show me how you did that.

00:51:13.501 --> 00:51:14.302 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

00:51:14.335 --> 00:51:16.903 position:27% line:83% align:start
Let my movements
tell you what to do.

00:51:16.937 --> 00:51:17.505 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ow!

00:51:17.538 --> 00:51:18.473 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
You follow me.

00:51:18.506 --> 00:51:19.640 position:13% line:89% align:start
Good luck with that, kid.

00:51:19.674 --> 00:51:21.542 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kumatetsu is one of
the most stubborn,

00:51:21.576 --> 00:51:23.378 position:21% line:83% align:start
self-centered Beasts
I've ever met.

00:51:23.411 --> 00:51:24.978 position:27% line:83% align:start
Following isn't
exactly something

00:51:25.011 --> 00:51:26.380 position:10% line:89% align:start
that comes naturally to him.

00:51:26.413 --> 00:51:29.483 position:19% line:83% align:start
He's never had anyone
to follow but himself.

00:51:29.516 --> 00:51:30.450 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ow!

00:51:30.484 --> 00:51:32.285 position:21% line:83% align:start
You have to let your
opponent be your guide!

00:51:32.319 --> 00:51:33.320 position:27% line:89% align:start
Ow! I'm trying!

00:51:33.353 --> 00:51:34.588 position:19% line:89% align:start
Well then, try harder!

00:51:34.621 --> 00:51:36.056 position:27% line:89% align:start
Why, you little!

00:51:36.089 --> 00:51:40.260 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snarls]

00:51:40.293 --> 00:51:42.027 position:16% line:89% align:start
Fine. Let's keep going.

00:51:42.061 --> 00:51:44.231 position:27% line:89% align:start
[BOTH grunting]

00:51:44.264 --> 00:51:47.567 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Haa... [grunts]

00:51:47.601 --> 00:51:49.135 position:38% line:89% align:start
Haaa...!

00:51:50.336 --> 00:51:51.705 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yaah!

00:51:51.738 --> 00:51:53.406 position:19% line:89% align:start
[BOY BEAST E grunting]

00:51:53.439 --> 00:51:54.708 position:27% line:89% align:start
Waaugh! [grunts]

00:51:54.741 --> 00:51:56.409 position:5% line:89% align:start
[BOY BEAST F, BOY BEAST G yell]

00:51:56.442 --> 00:51:59.078 position:24% line:89% align:start
[BOY BEASTS yell]

00:51:59.111 --> 00:52:00.646 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
I can still take you, human!

00:52:00.679 --> 00:52:01.180 position:35% line:89% align:start
Jiromaru.

00:52:01.213 --> 00:52:02.348 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that's my bet.

00:52:02.381 --> 00:52:03.315 position:24% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh. Mine, too.

00:52:03.349 --> 00:52:05.351 position:21% line:89% align:start
[JIROMARU grunting]

00:52:05.384 --> 00:52:06.152 position:44% line:89% align:start
You!

00:52:06.185 --> 00:52:07.520 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:52:08.754 --> 00:52:11.724 position:27% line:89% align:start
[BOTH grunting]

00:52:11.757 --> 00:52:13.992 position:16% line:89% align:start
[BOY & GIRL BEASTS gasp]

00:52:14.025 --> 00:52:14.693 position:24% line:89% align:start
[JIROMARU grunts]

00:52:14.727 --> 00:52:17.028 position:21% line:89% align:start
[SCARY BEASTS gasp]

00:52:17.061 --> 00:52:18.396 position:16% line:89% align:start
[BOY & GIRL BEASTS gasp]

00:52:22.534 --> 00:52:24.335 position:13% line:89% align:start
Wow, you're pretty strong!

00:52:24.369 --> 00:52:25.403 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:52:25.437 --> 00:52:27.071 position:13% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU] You're strong.
Strong guys are cool!

00:52:27.105 --> 00:52:29.240 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hey, you should come
hang out at my house!

00:52:29.274 --> 00:52:31.008 position:5% line:89% align:start
You'll like it! We've got candy!

00:52:31.041 --> 00:52:33.411 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you say?
Want to come over?

00:52:33.445 --> 00:52:34.646 position:38% line:89% align:start
Haa...!

00:52:34.679 --> 00:52:36.748 position:38% line:89% align:start
Finally.

00:52:36.781 --> 00:52:39.617 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hyah!

00:52:39.651 --> 00:52:41.185 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:52:41.218 --> 00:52:42.319 position:27% line:89% align:start
Slow down, guys.

00:52:42.352 --> 00:52:44.121 position:30% line:83% align:start
Take a breath.
This isn't a contest.

00:52:44.154 --> 00:52:46.123 position:13% line:89% align:start
I win. You do the dishes.

00:52:46.156 --> 00:52:47.458 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA groans]

00:52:54.531 --> 00:52:56.767 position:5% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] I can't believe it!
You've gotten so much taller.

00:52:56.800 --> 00:52:58.235 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you think so?

00:52:58.268 --> 00:52:59.001 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TATARA gasps]

00:52:59.035 --> 00:53:00.102 position:30% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

00:53:00.136 --> 00:53:02.539 position:19% line:89% align:start
