00:53:12.515 --> 00:53:15.418 position:19% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN] Hmm. He isn't
doing too badly, actually.

00:53:15.451 --> 00:53:16.519 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Not badly at all.

00:53:16.552 --> 00:53:19.388 position:16% line:83% align:start
Much better than I would
have expected from a human.

00:53:19.422 --> 00:53:22.191 position:16% line:83% align:start
