I'm most impressed with.

00:53:22.225 --> 00:53:22.792 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Huh?

00:53:22.825 --> 00:53:23.759 position:24% line:89% align:start
Can't you see it?

00:53:23.793 --> 00:53:26.127 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kumatetsu has grown
more than the boy has.

00:53:26.161 --> 00:53:28.798 position:19% line:83% align:start
His moves are sharper
and more refined.

00:53:28.831 --> 00:53:29.799 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're right, they are.

00:53:29.832 --> 00:53:33.401 position:16% line:83% align:start
Which is the master and
which the apprentice?

00:53:33.435 --> 00:53:36.404 position:30% line:89% align:start
[LORD laughs]

00:53:36.438 --> 00:53:41.309 position:10% line:83% align:start
You look taller and bigger,
So how old are you now?

00:53:41.343 --> 00:53:42.277 position:27% line:89% align:start
That was quick.

00:53:42.310 --> 00:53:44.044 position:10% line:83% align:start
I guess you really grew up,
now, didn't ya?

00:53:44.079 --> 00:53:46.146 position:19% line:89% align:start
Kids tend to do that.

00:53:51.453 --> 00:53:52.654 position:24% line:83% align:start
