Well, even so...

01:03:13.792 --> 01:03:15.293 position:10% line:89% align:start
What a miserable little man!

01:03:15.326 --> 01:03:18.229 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] It's impossible.
Let's just drop it.

01:03:18.263 --> 01:03:20.198 position:16% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE ACADEMIC CLERK]
Please! Hang on a second!

01:03:20.231 --> 01:03:22.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry about him.
I'll be happy to help you.

01:03:22.200 --> 01:03:24.835 position:7% line:83% align:start
There's always somebody giving
out a scholarship of some sort.

01:03:24.869 --> 01:03:27.671 position:5% line:83% align:start
And some companies even sponsor
students seeking a degree.

01:03:27.704 --> 01:03:29.740 position:16% line:83% align:start
Though earning one will
depend on your scores.

01:03:29.773 --> 01:03:32.109 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE gasps]
Thank you so much!

01:03:32.143 --> 01:03:34.379 position:7% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I really appreciate it.

01:03:34.412 --> 01:03:36.780 position:27% line:83% align:start
Math and science
will be on the exam.

01:03:36.814 --> 01:03:38.916 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've never studied
either before.

01:03:38.949 --> 01:03:39.983 position:33% line:89% align:start
Don't worry.

01:03:40.017 --> 01:03:41.785 position:16% line:83% align:start
That's what you have me
here for. I'll teach you.

01:03:41.819 --> 01:03:43.220 position:24% line:89% align:start
[intercom chimes]

01:03:43.253 --> 01:03:44.688 position:16% line:83% align:start
[MALE ACADEMIC CLERK B]
A residence registry card

01:03:44.721 --> 01:03:46.256 position:21% line:83% align:start
for college entrance
exams, right?

01:03:46.290 --> 01:03:47.723 position:10% line:89% align:start
Unfortunately, it looks like

01:03:47.757 --> 01:03:50.027 position:19% line:83% align:start
your old registration
has expired.

01:03:50.060 --> 01:03:51.095 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
I figured.

01:03:51.128 --> 01:03:53.297 position:16% line:83% align:start
However, it does appear
that your family registry

01:03:53.330 --> 01:03:54.364 position:27% line:89% align:start
is still valid,

01:03:54.398 --> 01:03:57.700 position:5% line:83% align:start
so it shouldn't be too difficult
to sort this out.

01:03:57.733 --> 01:04:00.304 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'll just need you to confirm
your father's address.

01:04:00.337 --> 01:04:02.138 position:16% line:89% align:start
Does that look correct?

01:04:05.108 --> 01:04:07.110 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
He and your mom split up, right?

01:04:07.143 --> 01:04:08.344 position:21% line:89% align:start
You lived with her.

01:04:08.377 --> 01:04:09.846 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Yeah, that's right.

01:04:09.879 --> 01:04:12.014 position:7% line:89% align:start
I had no idea where he lived.

01:04:12.048 --> 01:04:15.051 position:21% line:83% align:start
After all this time,
finding out was this easy?

01:04:15.084 --> 01:04:16.952 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
Are you going to see him?

01:04:16.986 --> 01:04:19.821 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] I don't know if
I should. He might not like it.

01:04:19.855 --> 01:04:22.657 position:30% line:83% align:start
He might have
forgotten all about me.

01:04:22.691 --> 01:04:25.894 position:27% line:89% align:start
But... Maybe...

01:04:35.237 --> 01:04:37.873 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
What should I write?

01:04:41.809 --> 01:04:43.010 position:16% line:89% align:start
Throw me the ball, Dad!

01:04:43.044 --> 01:04:44.945 position:27% line:83% align:start
[FATHER laughs]
Catch!

01:05:08.102 --> 01:05:09.203 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE SHOP WORKER]
Excuse me, sir!

01:05:09.236 --> 01:05:10.204 position:24% line:89% align:start
But is this yours?

01:05:10.237 --> 01:05:13.773 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Huh? It is! Guess I forgot it.

01:05:13.806 --> 01:05:15.476 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thank you for catching me.

01:05:15.509 --> 01:05:17.377 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE SHOP WORKER]
No problem.

01:05:19.879 --> 01:05:21.214 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Uh...

01:05:22.982 --> 01:05:24.817 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Yes?

01:05:24.851 --> 01:05:29.122 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do you know me?
It's been awhile, but, maybe...

01:05:40.933 --> 01:05:43.168 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Of course not.

01:05:43.202 --> 01:05:44.736 position:33% line:89% align:start
Never mind.

01:05:48.307 --> 01:05:52.277 position:19% line:89% align:start
[YOUNG BOYS laughing]

01:05:52.311 --> 01:05:53.844 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Ren...?

01:05:58.816 --> 01:06:01.819 position:27% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Ren! Is that you?

01:06:04.822 --> 01:06:06.157 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

01:06:07.458 --> 01:06:08.893 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
You've gotten so big!

01:06:08.926 --> 01:06:11.128 position:16% line:89% align:start
I didn't recognize you!

01:06:12.863 --> 01:06:14.198 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Where have you been?

01:06:14.232 --> 01:06:17.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh. Someone's been
looking after me.

01:06:17.834 --> 01:06:18.970 position:33% line:89% align:start
For a while.

01:06:19.003 --> 01:06:22.005 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
You're alive! Thank God!

01:06:22.038 --> 01:06:24.542 position:21% line:89% align:start
[REN'S FATHER sobs]

01:06:24.575 --> 01:06:26.510 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
I'm so sorry...

01:06:26.544 --> 01:06:28.979 position:24% line:83% align:start
I should have been
the one looking after you.

01:06:29.012 --> 01:06:30.313 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's okay.

01:06:30.347 --> 01:06:35.318 position:21% line:89% align:start
[REN'S FATHER sobs]

01:06:35.352 --> 01:06:38.288 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
Really? I'm so happy for you!

01:06:38.321 --> 01:06:39.923 position:27% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] Dad said
he didn't know about Mom

01:06:39.956 --> 01:06:41.458 position:24% line:89% align:start
until a lot later.

01:06:41.491 --> 01:06:44.527 position:13% line:83% align:start
When he heard I ran away,
he looked for me a long time.

01:06:44.561 --> 01:06:46.563 position:19% line:83% align:start
Even after the police
had given up.

01:06:46.596 --> 01:06:49.098 position:21% line:83% align:start
So I guess he didn't
forget about me.

01:06:49.131 --> 01:06:50.966 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
Nope.

01:06:51.000 --> 01:06:52.268 position:27% line:83% align:start
[GIRL STUDENT C]
Kaede!

01:06:52.301 --> 01:06:54.303 position:24% line:83% align:start
Who are you with?
Is that your boyfriend?

01:06:54.336 --> 01:06:55.204 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
He's my friend.

01:06:55.237 --> 01:06:56.138 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's his name?

01:06:56.171 --> 01:06:57.473 position:19% line:89% align:start
And where does he go?

01:06:57.506 --> 01:06:59.208 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
Just drop it, will you?

01:06:59.241 --> 01:07:00.976 position:30% line:89% align:start
[GIRLS laugh]

01:07:01.010 --> 01:07:03.379 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
I'm sorry.

01:07:03.412 --> 01:07:05.880 position:21% line:83% align:start
So, are things just
gonna be normal now?

01:07:05.914 --> 01:07:07.516 position:38% line:89% align:start
Normal?

01:07:07.549 --> 01:07:10.219 position:7% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] I'll live with family
like an ordinary guy.

01:07:10.252 --> 01:07:12.154 position:7% line:89% align:start
Study, find somewhere to work,

01:07:12.187 --> 01:07:15.023 position:16% line:83% align:start
come home after work and
sleep like an ordinary guy.

01:07:15.056 --> 01:07:16.492 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'll have an ordinary life.

01:07:16.525 --> 01:07:20.028 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's not something
I'd ever really expected.

01:07:20.061 --> 01:07:22.563 position:16% line:89% align:start
Except you seem unsure.

01:07:24.132 --> 01:07:26.434 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
Is it because of your master?

01:07:34.542 --> 01:07:36.210 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Where were you?

01:07:36.244 --> 01:07:38.879 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
We need to talk. It's serious.

01:07:38.912 --> 01:07:40.581 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
You haven't been training?

01:07:40.615 --> 01:07:42.082 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Listen. Lately, I--

01:07:42.115 --> 01:07:43.484 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
You've been what, goofing off?

01:07:43.518 --> 01:07:45.485 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Listen to what he has to say.

01:07:45.520 --> 01:07:48.088 position:10% line:89% align:start
First, explain this for me.

01:07:48.121 --> 01:07:50.090 position:5% line:89% align:start
I found it under your mattress.

01:07:50.123 --> 01:07:52.492 position:33% line:89% align:start
What is it?

01:07:52.526 --> 01:07:54.895 position:5% line:83% align:start
--I wanna go to a human school.
--[KUMATETSU] Huh?

01:07:54.928 --> 01:07:57.297 position:13% line:83% align:start
I want to learn the things
I can't learn here.

01:07:57.331 --> 01:07:59.066 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] You don't have
time for human school.

01:07:59.099 --> 01:08:01.201 position:27% line:83% align:start
You've got more
important things to do.

01:08:01.234 --> 01:08:02.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
Or don't you want
to become strong?

01:08:02.536 --> 01:08:03.603 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm already strong.

01:08:03.637 --> 01:08:05.171 position:10% line:89% align:start
Huh?! You're kidding, right?

01:08:05.204 --> 01:08:06.305 position:35% line:89% align:start
Kumatetsu.

01:08:06.339 --> 01:08:07.607 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm strong enough.

01:08:07.641 --> 01:08:11.110 position:21% line:83% align:start
Wanna show me which
part of you is strong? Huh?!

01:08:11.143 --> 01:08:14.013 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's always like this
when I try to talk to you.

01:08:14.046 --> 01:08:16.148 position:13% line:83% align:start
You don't even pretend to
listen to what I'm saying.

01:08:16.182 --> 01:08:17.116 position:16% line:89% align:start
You just start yelling.

01:08:17.149 --> 01:08:19.418 position:30% line:83% align:start
Tell me, brat!
Which part of you is strong?

01:08:19.452 --> 01:08:20.319 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Forget it.

01:08:20.353 --> 01:08:22.555 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Wait! Where are you going?

01:08:22.588 --> 01:08:24.457 position:30% line:83% align:start
Something else
I need to tell you.

01:08:24.490 --> 01:08:26.292 position:10% line:89% align:start
I know where my dad is now.

01:08:26.325 --> 01:08:29.194 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll go live with him.
I just decided.

01:08:30.663 --> 01:08:33.264 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Kyuta! Hold on!

01:08:33.298 --> 01:08:34.032 position:35% line:89% align:start
Don't go.

01:08:34.065 --> 01:08:34.600 position:38% line:89% align:start
Move it.

01:08:34.633 --> 01:08:37.235 position:38% line:89% align:start
Make me!

01:08:37.268 --> 01:08:38.603 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

01:08:42.374 --> 01:08:43.908 position:35% line:89% align:start
Don't go!

01:08:45.176 --> 01:08:49.079 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Kyuta! Kyuta!

01:08:50.981 --> 01:08:52.450 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
Well, how did it go?

01:08:52.484 --> 01:08:54.419 position:13% line:89% align:start
Did you make up your mind?

01:08:54.452 --> 01:08:56.086 position:21% line:89% align:start
Still not sure, huh?

01:08:56.120 --> 01:08:58.590 position:24% line:83% align:start
It doesn't really
matter anymore.

01:08:58.623 --> 01:09:02.593 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm meeting up with my dad now.
That ought to settle everything.

01:09:02.626 --> 01:09:03.994 position:16% line:89% align:start
You can take it slower.

01:09:04.027 --> 01:09:06.196 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Why would I need to?

01:09:06.230 --> 01:09:08.499 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, I'll be at
the library all day.

01:09:08.532 --> 01:09:10.434 position:5% line:89% align:start
Come by and see me if you want.

01:09:12.536 --> 01:09:14.671 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
No! No, no, no!

01:09:14.705 --> 01:09:15.606 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TRAINEE BEAST A]
We're sorry.

01:09:15.639 --> 01:09:17.006 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Why can't you get it right?!

01:09:17.039 --> 01:09:18.074 position:21% line:89% align:start
Are you all idiots?

01:09:18.107 --> 01:09:19.075 position:24% line:89% align:start
We're sorry, sir!

01:09:19.108 --> 01:09:21.077 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Stop apologizing!

01:09:21.110 --> 01:09:22.145 position:27% line:83% align:start
[TRAINEE BEASTS]
We're sorry, sir!

01:09:22.178 --> 01:09:23.614 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Bah!

01:09:23.647 --> 01:09:25.548 position:21% line:89% align:start
Idiots! All of them!

01:09:25.581 --> 01:09:28.651 position:7% line:83% align:start
I can't believe Kyuta's father
showed up after all this time.

01:09:28.684 --> 01:09:31.187 position:13% line:83% align:start
Is he really going to live
in the human world now?

01:09:31.220 --> 01:09:33.222 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Of course he is. You heard him.

01:09:33.256 --> 01:09:36.626 position:5% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] Hm. But without him
around, Kumatetsu will go back

01:09:36.659 --> 01:09:38.327 position:27% line:83% align:start
to being sloppy
and irresponsible.

01:09:38.361 --> 01:09:39.595 position:7% line:89% align:start
Heh. What do you mean "will"?

01:09:39.629 --> 01:09:40.730 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Shut up!

01:09:40.763 --> 01:09:43.131 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're gonna crack
someone's skull!

01:09:44.232 --> 01:09:45.668 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
This is hard on him.

01:09:45.701 --> 01:09:48.336 position:16% line:83% align:start
He thought of himself as
Kyuta's father, you know.

01:09:48.370 --> 01:09:50.205 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
He did?

01:09:50.238 --> 01:09:52.340 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU sighs]

01:09:52.374 --> 01:09:53.708 position:38% line:89% align:start
[growls]

01:09:59.748 --> 01:10:00.882 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ren!

01:10:02.250 --> 01:10:05.186 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought we could make a
ham omelet for dinner tonight.

01:10:05.219 --> 01:10:06.555 position:19% line:89% align:start
Does that sound good?

01:10:11.091 --> 01:10:12.561 position:10% line:89% align:start
[REN'S FATHER clears throat]

01:10:12.594 --> 01:10:15.196 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
So, tell me about this man

01:10:15.229 --> 01:10:18.232 position:7% line:83% align:start
who's been taking care of you.
I wanna hear all about him.

01:10:18.265 --> 01:10:19.366 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Huh?

01:10:19.400 --> 01:10:21.101 position:35% line:83% align:start
Of course,
I wanna meet him, too.

01:10:21.135 --> 01:10:23.003 position:24% line:83% align:start
So I can thank him
for everything.

01:10:23.037 --> 01:10:25.573 position:19% line:83% align:start
And let him know that
you'll be living with me now.

01:10:25.606 --> 01:10:27.106 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hold on a second.

01:10:27.141 --> 01:10:29.310 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Hm? Why, what's wrong?

01:10:29.343 --> 01:10:31.177 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
It's just--

01:10:31.211 --> 01:10:35.014 position:19% line:83% align:start
This is moving really
quickly, you know?

01:10:35.048 --> 01:10:37.685 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
You're right. Sorry.

01:10:37.718 --> 01:10:41.287 position:7% line:83% align:start
See, the thing is, time passes
quicker the older you get.

01:10:41.321 --> 01:10:44.624 position:30% line:83% align:start
Sounds weird,
I know, but it's true.

01:10:44.657 --> 01:10:47.327 position:24% line:83% align:start
So, for me, living
with you and your mom,

01:10:47.360 --> 01:10:49.796 position:19% line:83% align:start
well, that feels like
it was only yesterday.

01:10:49.829 --> 01:10:51.331 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yesterday?

01:10:51.364 --> 01:10:52.699 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Give me another shot.

01:10:52.732 --> 01:10:55.535 position:7% line:89% align:start
We'll start fresh, you and me.

01:10:55.568 --> 01:10:58.170 position:10% line:83% align:start
From now on, I'll hang back
and follow your lead.

01:10:58.203 --> 01:11:00.807 position:16% line:83% align:start
I know these past years
have been tough.

01:11:00.840 --> 01:11:03.108 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
How can we ever start fresh?

01:11:03.141 --> 01:11:04.042 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
Huh?

01:11:04.076 --> 01:11:06.612 position:16% line:83% align:start
And what makes you think
I've had it tough?

01:11:06.645 --> 01:11:08.780 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you know
about me or my life?

01:11:08.814 --> 01:11:09.615 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ren.

01:11:09.648 --> 01:11:11.149 position:30% line:83% align:start
You don't know
anything about me!

01:11:11.183 --> 01:11:12.084 position:24% line:89% align:start
You weren't there!

01:11:12.117 --> 01:11:14.353 position:33% line:89% align:start
I-I'm sorry.

01:11:20.859 --> 01:11:22.260 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA sighs]

01:11:22.293 --> 01:11:24.161 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
You don't know. How could you?

01:11:24.195 --> 01:11:26.297 position:10% line:89% align:start
I haven't told you anything.

01:11:26.330 --> 01:11:28.332 position:21% line:89% align:start
Sorry. I have to go.

01:11:28.366 --> 01:11:29.133 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REN'S FATHER]
No dinner?

01:11:29.166 --> 01:11:30.601 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
No.

01:11:30.635 --> 01:11:34.572 position:7% line:83% align:start
Ren, I meant what I said about
following your lead, okay?

01:11:34.605 --> 01:11:36.340 position:16% line:89% align:start
But remember something!

01:11:36.374 --> 01:11:38.676 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you ever need me,
I'll do anything for you.

01:11:38.709 --> 01:11:40.711 position:35% line:89% align:start
Anything!

01:11:40.745 --> 01:11:42.280 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ren!

01:11:46.651 --> 01:11:48.519 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
What's wrong with me?

01:11:48.553 --> 01:11:50.353 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why did I go off
on Dad like that?

