01:21:24.338 --> 01:21:26.673 position:5% line:89% align:start
You've got a match to win, here!

01:21:26.706 --> 01:21:29.943 position:13% line:83% align:start
You're wasting your time.
I didn't need you to come.

01:21:29.976 --> 01:21:31.811 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm not gonna lose!

01:21:31.845 --> 01:21:35.715 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU roars]

01:21:35.748 --> 01:21:37.884 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

01:21:37.917 --> 01:21:38.384 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN grunts]

01:21:38.418 --> 01:21:42.155 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

01:21:42.188 --> 01:21:43.722 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

01:21:45.024 --> 01:21:46.359 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

01:21:46.392 --> 01:21:48.027 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TATARA sighs]

01:21:48.061 --> 01:21:49.329 position:19% line:89% align:start
I guess it's not over.

01:21:49.362 --> 01:21:51.830 position:27% line:83% align:start
This is starting
to get interesting.

01:21:53.699 --> 01:21:54.099 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

01:21:54.133 --> 01:21:56.802 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN growls]

01:21:56.835 --> 01:21:58.203 position:33% line:89% align:start
[BOTH grunt]

01:21:58.237 --> 01:21:59.938 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunting]

01:21:59.972 --> 01:22:02.774 position:30% line:83% align:start
To the right!
Then back! Now counter!

01:22:02.808 --> 01:22:04.309 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunting]

01:22:04.343 --> 01:22:05.811 position:33% line:89% align:start
Under! Over!

01:22:05.844 --> 01:22:08.914 position:19% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU chuckles]
--[IOZEN grunts]

01:22:08.947 --> 01:22:12.217 position:30% line:83% align:start
He's smiling.
It's like he's enjoying this.

01:22:12.251 --> 01:22:13.285 position:19% line:89% align:start
The look on his face--

01:22:13.318 --> 01:22:15.320 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's the same as when
he's training with Kyuta.

01:22:15.354 --> 01:22:18.357 position:24% line:83% align:start
But it's a match.
A really important one.

01:22:18.390 --> 01:22:20.725 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KOKURAN DOJIN] His mind has
transcended the present.

01:22:20.758 --> 01:22:22.994 position:21% line:83% align:start
He can react before
his opponent moves.

01:22:23.027 --> 01:22:25.296 position:30% line:83% align:start
He's achieved
complete concentration.

01:22:25.329 --> 01:22:26.731 position:21% line:89% align:start
A state of non-ego.

01:22:26.764 --> 01:22:29.066 position:19% line:83% align:start
Kumatetsu could never
have won on his own.

01:22:29.100 --> 01:22:31.936 position:10% line:83% align:start
But... with the two of them
fighting together.

01:22:31.969 --> 01:22:33.703 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunting]

01:22:33.737 --> 01:22:35.239 position:10% line:89% align:start
Come on, Dad. You can do it!

01:22:35.273 --> 01:22:38.142 position:10% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN, KUMATETSU grunting]

01:22:38.176 --> 01:22:40.110 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ah! He's really losing!

01:22:40.144 --> 01:22:41.945 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Shut up!

01:22:41.978 --> 01:22:43.381 position:24% line:89% align:start
What's that for?!

01:22:43.414 --> 01:22:48.118 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kyuta. Stupid human!
Always interfering!

01:22:48.151 --> 01:22:50.453 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN yells]

01:22:50.487 --> 01:22:53.190 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunting]

01:22:53.223 --> 01:22:56.293 position:24% line:83% align:start
You've gotta push!
Don't let him overpower you!

01:22:56.326 --> 01:22:58.328 position:5% line:89% align:start
Give him everything you've got!

01:22:58.361 --> 01:23:00.030 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU yells]

01:23:01.764 --> 01:23:03.099 position:33% line:89% align:start
[BOTH grunt]

01:23:09.138 --> 01:23:09.905 position:35% line:89% align:start
Now, kick!

01:23:09.939 --> 01:23:11.807 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU roars]

01:23:11.840 --> 01:23:13.409 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Wha--?!

01:23:13.442 --> 01:23:14.877 position:33% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU]

01:23:14.910 --> 01:23:16.378 position:24% line:89% align:start
[gasping, yelling]

01:23:16.412 --> 01:23:17.780 position:33% line:89% align:start
[LORD sighs]

01:23:17.813 --> 01:23:19.148 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU growls]

01:23:19.181 --> 01:23:21.150 position:27% line:89% align:start
One last punch!

01:23:21.183 --> 01:23:23.953 position:38% line:89% align:start
[roars]

01:23:36.130 --> 01:23:38.032 position:27% line:83% align:start
[BEAST REFEREE]
One.

01:23:38.066 --> 01:23:39.834 position:44% line:89% align:start
Two.

01:23:39.867 --> 01:23:41.869 position:41% line:89% align:start
Three.

01:23:41.903 --> 01:23:43.538 position:41% line:89% align:start
Four.

01:23:43.571 --> 01:23:47.141 position:35% line:89% align:start
Five. Six.

01:23:47.175 --> 01:23:52.180 position:21% line:89% align:start
Seven. Eight. Nine.

01:23:52.213 --> 01:23:53.981 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ten!

01:23:54.014 --> 01:23:56.917 position:24% line:83% align:start
And the winner of
the match is Kumatetsu!

01:23:56.950 --> 01:24:01.255 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

01:24:05.892 --> 01:24:07.227 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN groans]

01:24:18.070 --> 01:24:19.473 position:30% line:83% align:start
You really had
me worried there.

01:24:19.506 --> 01:24:21.974 position:27% line:83% align:start
I never ask you
to worry about me.

01:24:22.008 --> 01:24:23.510 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm still surprised you won.

01:24:23.543 --> 01:24:25.177 position:16% line:89% align:start
Really? 'Cause I'm not.

01:24:25.211 --> 01:24:27.480 position:5% line:89% align:start
Idiot. The ref made it to nine.

01:24:27.514 --> 01:24:29.248 position:38% line:89% align:start
Shut up.

01:24:31.150 --> 01:24:34.053 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

01:24:34.086 --> 01:24:35.554 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

01:24:35.588 --> 01:24:37.156 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

01:24:37.189 --> 01:24:40.859 position:16% line:83% align:start
[BEAST REFEREE] All hail
the new lord of Jutengai!

01:24:40.892 --> 01:24:41.594 position:21% line:89% align:start
[cheering continues]

01:24:41.627 --> 01:24:43.928 position:13% line:89% align:start
[TATARA, HYAKUSHUBO laugh]

01:24:43.962 --> 01:24:45.830 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

01:24:45.864 --> 01:24:48.099 position:16% line:89% align:start
[SCARY BEASTS cheering]

01:24:48.133 --> 01:24:49.868 position:21% line:89% align:start
He is a worthy son.

01:24:51.236 --> 01:24:53.071 position:35% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

01:24:53.104 --> 01:24:56.207 position:27% line:89% align:start
[LORD chuckles]

01:24:56.241 --> 01:24:57.942 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh...?

01:24:57.976 --> 01:25:01.313 position:19% line:89% align:start
The sword. It's gone!

01:25:01.346 --> 01:25:02.547 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:25:02.580 --> 01:25:04.115 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

01:25:11.556 --> 01:25:14.358 position:10% line:89% align:start
Huh. What's this red stuff?

01:25:16.060 --> 01:25:19.029 position:10% line:89% align:start
Kyuta... what's going on...?

01:25:19.063 --> 01:25:22.266 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO cackles]

01:25:22.299 --> 01:25:24.068 position:30% line:89% align:start
[IOZEN gasps]

01:25:24.101 --> 01:25:25.135 position:30% line:89% align:start
Look, Father!

01:25:25.169 --> 01:25:27.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
With the power of my
telekinesis and your sword,

01:25:27.538 --> 01:25:28.905 position:16% line:89% align:start
we've made things right!

01:25:28.938 --> 01:25:30.240 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're the true winner!

01:25:30.274 --> 01:25:32.309 position:21% line:83% align:start
A lazy slob like him
couldn't defeat you--

01:25:32.343 --> 01:25:34.143 position:16% line:89% align:start
not in a million years!

01:25:34.177 --> 01:25:36.347 position:13% line:89% align:start
You know it's true, Kyuta!

01:25:36.380 --> 01:25:38.848 position:35% line:89% align:start
You know!

01:25:40.483 --> 01:25:42.218 position:16% line:89% align:start
Please stop, Ichirohiko!

01:25:42.251 --> 01:25:44.987 position:33% line:83% align:start
This is it!
One more push and it's finished.

01:25:45.021 --> 01:25:47.223 position:24% line:89% align:start
Watch me, Father!

01:25:47.256 --> 01:25:48.057 position:33% line:89% align:start
[squelching]

01:25:48.091 --> 01:25:50.159 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[KUMATETSU groans]
--[BEASTS gasp]

01:25:50.193 --> 01:25:53.463 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

01:25:55.631 --> 01:25:58.301 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO laughs]

01:25:58.334 --> 01:26:00.636 position:10% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO] Finally getting
what you deserve, Kyuta!

01:26:00.670 --> 01:26:03.439 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's over! All hail
the new lord, my father--

01:26:03.473 --> 01:26:05.907 position:27% line:83% align:start
You damned fool!
The match is over and done with!

01:26:05.941 --> 01:26:13.915 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO laughs]

01:26:13.949 --> 01:26:16.451 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TATARA gasps]
What is that thing?!

01:26:16.485 --> 01:26:17.319 position:38% line:89% align:start
A hole?

01:26:17.352 --> 01:26:19.521 position:24% line:89% align:start
Resist it, Kyuta!

01:26:26.060 --> 01:26:27.361 position:30% line:89% align:start
How dare you!

01:26:27.395 --> 01:26:28.396 position:27% line:89% align:start
[JIROMARU gasps]

01:26:28.429 --> 01:26:30.431 position:30% line:89% align:start
How dare you!

01:26:30.464 --> 01:26:32.333 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hold firm! Reject the Darkness!

01:26:32.366 --> 01:26:33.300 position:33% line:89% align:start
Please, no!

01:26:33.334 --> 01:26:36.670 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not you, too, Kyuta!
How is this happening?!

01:26:36.704 --> 01:26:38.305 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA snarls]

01:26:38.339 --> 01:26:41.275 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

01:26:42.576 --> 01:26:44.345 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

01:26:44.378 --> 01:26:45.979 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

01:26:46.012 --> 01:26:47.348 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:26:49.517 --> 01:26:51.050 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO whimpers]

01:26:57.590 --> 01:27:00.326 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Kyuta...

01:27:00.360 --> 01:27:02.562 position:33% line:89% align:start
I hate you.

01:27:02.595 --> 01:27:03.663 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's happening.

01:27:03.696 --> 01:27:07.333 position:27% line:83% align:start
The Darkness is
swallowing Ichirohiko!

01:27:07.367 --> 01:27:10.503 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
I will never forgive you.

01:27:15.107 --> 01:27:16.975 position:38% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
Wha--?

01:27:17.009 --> 01:27:19.746 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where? Where... is he?

01:27:19.779 --> 01:27:23.682 position:38% line:89% align:start
[pants]

01:27:23.715 --> 01:27:27.219 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey. Quit playing.

01:27:27.252 --> 01:27:28.253 position:38% line:89% align:start
Get up.

01:27:28.287 --> 01:27:31.056 position:33% line:89% align:start
Just get up.

01:27:36.395 --> 01:27:38.397 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Kyuta.

01:27:38.430 --> 01:27:40.231 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kyuta!

01:27:40.264 --> 01:27:41.065 position:41% line:89% align:start
Slow!

01:27:41.098 --> 01:27:42.501 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're always too slow!

01:27:42.534 --> 01:27:45.369 position:27% line:83% align:start
Get up already.
Time to practice!

01:27:46.637 --> 01:27:50.174 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA groans]

01:27:50.208 --> 01:27:53.511 position:24% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaking]

01:27:53.544 --> 01:27:54.712 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Chico...?

01:27:54.745 --> 01:27:56.714 position:24% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaking]

01:27:56.747 --> 01:27:59.049 position:24% line:83% align:start
What's happening?
What's wrong?

01:27:59.082 --> 01:28:03.488 position:24% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaking]

01:28:03.521 --> 01:28:05.055 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:28:08.525 --> 01:28:12.229 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU groans]

01:28:12.262 --> 01:28:16.299 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

01:28:16.333 --> 01:28:20.370 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sobs]

01:28:22.672 --> 01:28:24.106 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
I'm sorry...

01:28:24.139 --> 01:28:27.176 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ichirohiko, I'm sorry.

01:28:27.209 --> 01:28:29.613 position:7% line:83% align:start
[LORD] A Beast could never be
gifted with telekinesis

01:28:29.646 --> 01:28:31.815 position:33% line:83% align:start
as strongly
as Ichirohiko was.

01:28:31.848 --> 01:28:35.117 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's obvious that his power
was augmented by the Darkness

01:28:35.150 --> 01:28:37.219 position:24% line:83% align:start
that dwells within
the human heart.

01:28:37.253 --> 01:28:39.455 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Sir, are you saying...?

01:28:39.488 --> 01:28:42.258 position:16% line:83% align:start
Have you known the truth
about this whole time?

01:28:42.291 --> 01:28:46.060 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, Iozen. I'm waiting
for an explanation.

01:28:52.568 --> 01:28:59.775 position:30% line:89% align:start
[baby crying]

01:28:59.808 --> 01:29:08.750 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crying continues]

01:29:08.783 --> 01:29:10.184 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
In that moment,

01:29:10.218 --> 01:29:13.354 position:24% line:83% align:start
I decided to raise
him as my own son.

01:29:13.388 --> 01:29:16.424 position:5% line:83% align:start
I would tell nobody of the truth
of how I had found him.

01:29:16.457 --> 01:29:18.191 position:13% line:83% align:start
I knew about the Darkness,
of course,

01:29:18.225 --> 01:29:20.227 position:19% line:83% align:start
but I assumed that if
I raised him correctly,

01:29:20.260 --> 01:29:22.730 position:16% line:89% align:start
it would remain dormant.

01:29:22.764 --> 01:29:26.700 position:19% line:83% align:start
Thinking about it now,
I realize what a fool I was.

01:29:26.733 --> 01:29:29.736 position:13% line:89% align:start
What a presumptuous fool.

01:29:29.770 --> 01:29:31.471 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
What's wrong with my tusks?

01:29:31.505 --> 01:29:33.607 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why aren't they growing
like yours, father?

01:29:33.640 --> 01:29:37.311 position:13% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN] Don't worry, son.
They will one day.

01:29:37.344 --> 01:29:38.845 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
What's wrong with my snout?

01:29:38.879 --> 01:29:41.314 position:21% line:83% align:start
Why isn't it growing
like yours, father?

01:29:41.347 --> 01:29:42.716 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Don't worry, son.

01:29:42.749 --> 01:29:44.785 position:27% line:89% align:start
It will one day.

01:29:44.818 --> 01:29:47.854 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Father. Who am I, really?

01:29:47.888 --> 01:29:50.523 position:38% line:83% align:start
[IOZEN]
Ichirohiko, listen to me.

01:29:50.556 --> 01:29:53.125 position:27% line:83% align:start
You are my son.
Never doubt that.

01:29:53.159 --> 01:29:56.362 position:13% line:89% align:start
You are the son of Iozen.

01:29:56.395 --> 01:29:58.197 position:21% line:83% align:start
[LORD] The more you
tried to convince him,

01:29:58.230 --> 01:30:00.132 position:10% line:89% align:start
the more he doubted himself.

01:30:00.166 --> 01:30:02.868 position:7% line:83% align:start
That doubt festered inside him
like an unclean wound.

01:30:02.902 --> 01:30:06.472 position:21% line:83% align:start
It became anger and
strengthened the Darkness.

01:30:06.505 --> 01:30:08.173 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tragic, is it not?

01:30:08.206 --> 01:30:10.208 position:24% line:83% align:start
That the peaceful
world of Beasts

01:30:10.241 --> 01:30:14.212 position:13% line:83% align:start
could create such a great
hole in a human's heart.

01:30:14.245 --> 01:30:16.448 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JIROMARU]
Who cares about all that?

01:30:16.481 --> 01:30:18.683 position:27% line:83% align:start
I may not always
be the smartest guy.

01:30:18.717 --> 01:30:21.653 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't know where my brother's
from or what's wrong with him,

01:30:21.686 --> 01:30:24.389 position:16% line:83% align:start
but I do know that he's
my brother, no matter what!

01:30:24.422 --> 01:30:25.890 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, Jiromaru.

01:30:25.924 --> 01:30:27.191 position:30% line:89% align:start
Lord, tell me.

01:30:27.224 --> 01:30:29.293 position:27% line:83% align:start
Is there nothing
I can do to help my son?

01:30:29.327 --> 01:30:30.428 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm responsible!

01:30:30.462 --> 01:30:31.696 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm the one who
brought him here.

01:30:31.730 --> 01:30:35.265 position:5% line:83% align:start
Can't I bring him back again and
find a way to make him whole?

01:30:35.299 --> 01:30:38.737 position:5% line:83% align:start
You must realize that Ichirohiko
is no longer the boy you knew.

01:30:38.770 --> 01:30:40.638 position:16% line:89% align:start
He is lost and drifting.

01:30:40.671 --> 01:30:42.439 position:7% line:89% align:start
No one can do anything for him

01:30:42.473 --> 01:30:45.576 position:16% line:83% align:start
unless the Darkness that
possesses him is driven out.

01:30:48.712 --> 01:30:50.247 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Kyuta.

01:30:52.215 --> 01:30:55.318 position:16% line:83% align:start
Are you really going to
run out on Kumatetsu?

01:30:56.419 --> 01:30:57.253 position:38% line:89% align:start
[TATARA]

01:30:57.286 --> 01:30:59.590 position:35% line:83% align:start
You idiot!
Seeking revenge, are you?!

01:30:59.623 --> 01:31:01.792 position:27% line:83% align:start
Just what do you
hope to accomplish?!

01:31:01.825 --> 01:31:03.359 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Maybe we should all stay calm.

01:31:03.393 --> 01:31:04.962 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
I will not stay calm!

01:31:04.995 --> 01:31:06.663 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm not always as
nice and friendly

01:31:06.696 --> 01:31:08.598 position:24% line:83% align:start
as the rest of you
seem to think I am!

01:31:08.631 --> 01:31:10.633 position:21% line:83% align:start
