lying close to death!

01:31:10.667 --> 01:31:12.535 position:7% line:89% align:start
Haven't you learned anything?!

01:31:18.608 --> 01:31:19.942 position:24% line:89% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO sighs]

01:31:22.477 --> 01:31:25.280 position:13% line:83% align:start
You're still going to go,
though, aren't you?

01:31:27.449 --> 01:31:29.551 position:10% line:89% align:start
Thank you for yelling at me.

01:31:29.584 --> 01:31:32.454 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm glad you
care enough to do it.

01:31:32.487 --> 01:31:34.856 position:21% line:83% align:start
But I'm not leaving
because I want revenge.

01:31:34.890 --> 01:31:37.526 position:7% line:89% align:start
Ichirohiko and I are the same.

01:31:37.559 --> 01:31:41.496 position:5% line:83% align:start
I could easily have been the one
swallowed by Darkness today,

01:31:41.530 --> 01:31:43.365 position:16% line:89% align:start
but in the end, I wasn't

01:31:43.398 --> 01:31:44.933 position:19% line:83% align:start
because of the people
I was lucky enough

01:31:44.966 --> 01:31:46.868 position:16% line:89% align:start
to have been raised by.

01:31:46.902 --> 01:31:49.403 position:10% line:89% align:start
Including you. Both of you.

01:31:49.437 --> 01:31:50.906 position:33% line:89% align:start
So, thanks.

01:31:50.939 --> 01:31:53.607 position:13% line:89% align:start
Kyuta, please... Listen...

01:31:53.641 --> 01:31:57.411 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can't stay here.
I have to do something.

01:31:57.445 --> 01:32:00.247 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ichirohiko's Darkness
is mine, as well.

01:32:00.281 --> 01:32:02.316 position:33% line:89% align:start
We share it.

01:32:02.349 --> 01:32:05.419 position:5% line:89% align:start
Please understand. I have to go.

01:32:05.453 --> 01:32:06.987 position:27% line:89% align:start
Look after him.

01:32:08.456 --> 01:32:09.156 position:24% line:89% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO sighs]

01:32:09.190 --> 01:32:11.424 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Of course we understand!

01:32:11.458 --> 01:32:15.261 position:10% line:83% align:start
You do what you need to do.
Leave Kumatetsu to us!

01:32:15.295 --> 01:32:19.332 position:24% line:83% align:start
You get going now.
We've got it covered.

01:32:19.365 --> 01:32:20.000 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's okay.

01:32:20.034 --> 01:32:25.872 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TATARA sobs]

01:32:39.052 --> 01:32:41.054 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO] He believes
he was saved from the Darkness

01:32:41.087 --> 01:32:43.789 position:7% line:89% align:start
by the people who raised him?

01:32:43.823 --> 01:32:44.790 position:33% line:89% align:start
Us included?

01:32:44.823 --> 01:32:47.593 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm still not really sure
how that happened.

01:32:47.626 --> 01:32:49.528 position:24% line:83% align:start
We did spend a lot
of time around him,

01:32:49.561 --> 01:32:51.597 position:24% line:83% align:start
ever since he was
just a little boy.

01:32:51.630 --> 01:32:52.664 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

01:32:52.698 --> 01:32:56.001 position:13% line:83% align:start
I remember him back then.
He was a cocky brat.

01:32:56.034 --> 01:32:57.202 position:30% line:83% align:start
We went to see
him every day,

01:32:57.236 --> 01:33:00.005 position:7% line:83% align:start
even though he was a human and
someone else's apprentice.

01:33:00.038 --> 01:33:01.807 position:33% line:83% align:start
And gave him
our sage advice,

01:33:01.840 --> 01:33:04.009 position:21% line:83% align:start
not that he was ever
grateful for it.

01:33:04.042 --> 01:33:07.612 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now suddenly, here he is
looking so tall and grown up.

01:33:07.645 --> 01:33:10.782 position:21% line:83% align:start
Making decisions on
his own like an adult.

01:33:12.950 --> 01:33:14.719 position:7% line:89% align:start
I couldn't be prouder of him.

01:33:14.752 --> 01:33:16.821 position:21% line:89% align:start
No. Neither could I.

01:33:18.723 --> 01:33:19.724 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU groans]

01:33:19.757 --> 01:33:20.525 position:33% line:89% align:start
[BOTH gasp]

01:33:20.558 --> 01:33:21.726 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

01:33:21.759 --> 01:33:23.293 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Kumatetsu!

01:33:44.447 --> 01:33:45.682 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
It's Ren.

01:33:45.715 --> 01:33:47.918 position:7% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE NEWS REPORTER] This is
just the latest in a long line

01:33:47.951 --> 01:33:49.586 position:13% line:89% align:start
of credit card fraud cases

01:33:49.619 --> 01:33:51.621 position:21% line:83% align:start
the police have been
investigating this year.

01:33:51.655 --> 01:33:53.790 position:10% line:83% align:start
Officials say that the rise
in white collar crime

01:33:53.824 --> 01:33:56.725 position:7% line:83% align:start
will likely continue worldwide
as technology progresses

01:33:56.759 --> 01:33:59.029 position:16% line:83% align:start
beyond the scope of what
law enforcement agents

01:33:59.062 --> 01:34:00.496 position:19% line:89% align:start
are able to cope with.

01:34:00.529 --> 01:34:01.697 position:10% line:89% align:start
More and more frequently...

01:34:03.532 --> 01:34:06.035 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] Here. I want you
to hold onto this.

01:34:06.068 --> 01:34:07.436 position:35% line:89% align:start
Your book?

01:34:07.469 --> 01:34:08.571 position:24% line:89% align:start
Why? What's wrong?

01:34:08.604 --> 01:34:11.574 position:16% line:83% align:start
I can't explain now, but
there's something I need to do.

01:34:11.607 --> 01:34:14.109 position:5% line:89% align:start
It could turn out badly for me,

01:34:14.143 --> 01:34:16.611 position:13% line:83% align:start
and if it does, I probably
won't see you again.

01:34:16.645 --> 01:34:18.047 position:33% line:89% align:start
So take it.

01:34:18.080 --> 01:34:19.849 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let me help you.

01:34:19.882 --> 01:34:21.884 position:10% line:89% align:start
