01:34:21.917 --> 01:34:22.885 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't you see?

01:34:22.918 --> 01:34:25.420 position:19% line:83% align:start
You helped me realize
how big the world is.

01:34:25.453 --> 01:34:27.089 position:19% line:83% align:start
You gave me the chance
to learn things

01:34:27.122 --> 01:34:28.857 position:5% line:89% align:start
I never would have without you.

01:34:28.890 --> 01:34:31.459 position:13% line:83% align:start
And you can keep learning!
Please don't do this!

01:34:31.492 --> 01:34:32.827 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
I have to go now.

01:34:32.861 --> 01:34:35.129 position:5% line:89% align:start
But I'm glad I got to know you.

01:34:35.163 --> 01:34:36.396 position:41% line:89% align:start
And...

01:34:36.431 --> 01:34:37.966 position:10% line:89% align:start
Well, thanks for everything.

01:34:37.999 --> 01:34:40.835 position:35% line:83% align:start
Don't go!
Just tell me what's wrong.

01:34:40.869 --> 01:34:44.605 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sure together we can
figure out something.

01:34:44.638 --> 01:34:46.406 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

01:34:46.440 --> 01:34:47.774 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
Kyuta!

01:34:50.510 --> 01:34:51.612 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:34:51.645 --> 01:34:53.013 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
I hate you.

01:34:53.046 --> 01:34:54.182 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE gasps]

01:34:54.215 --> 01:34:57.017 position:30% line:83% align:start
