You ruin everything.

01:34:57.050 --> 01:34:58.652 position:16% line:89% align:start
This can't happen here!

01:34:58.685 --> 01:35:00.087 position:30% line:89% align:start
What is that?

01:35:01.855 --> 01:35:03.824 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
It's dangerous. Go.

01:35:03.857 --> 01:35:07.627 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE whimpers]

01:35:07.660 --> 01:35:09.662 position:19% line:89% align:start
