01:35:09.695 --> 01:35:12.498 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE whines]

01:35:12.531 --> 01:35:13.200 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
I'm not letting go.

01:35:13.233 --> 01:35:14.667 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA growls]

01:35:14.700 --> 01:35:16.936 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

01:35:16.969 --> 01:35:18.504 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Okay.

