[ICHIROHIKO yells]

01:35:48.066 --> 01:35:50.635 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

01:35:50.669 --> 01:35:56.174 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO giggles]

