--[KYUTA yells]
--[ICHIROHIKO gasps]

01:35:59.144 --> 01:36:00.778 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA growls]

01:36:00.811 --> 01:36:03.014 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO grunts]

01:36:03.048 --> 01:36:07.751 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO chuckles]

01:36:07.785 --> 01:36:09.119 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

01:36:11.956 --> 01:36:14.491 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA screams]

01:36:16.260 --> 01:36:17.995 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

01:36:19.296 --> 01:36:20.931 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE gasps]
Are you okay?!

01:36:20.965 --> 01:36:24.801 position:13% line:89% align:start
[CROWD gasping, screaming]

01:36:24.834 --> 01:36:25.970 position:19% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA groans, gasps]

01:36:30.039 --> 01:36:32.942 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Quick! Let's get outta here.

01:36:32.976 --> 01:36:34.911 position:16% line:89% align:start
Lead him somewhere else.

01:36:40.817 --> 01:36:42.919 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
A whale, huh?

01:36:44.988 --> 01:36:46.122 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Turn around!

01:36:46.155 --> 01:36:48.257 position:13% line:89% align:start
