01:36:57.766 --> 01:36:58.567 position:30% line:89% align:start
What is that?

01:36:58.600 --> 01:37:00.068 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MALE PEDESTRIAN D]
A big shadow?

01:37:11.645 --> 01:37:12.580 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE ONLOOKER B]
It looks like a--

01:37:12.613 --> 01:37:16.051 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE ONLOOKER B]
