[CROWD gasping]

01:37:42.376 --> 01:37:43.310 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE, KYUTA gasp]

01:37:43.344 --> 01:37:45.346 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE DRIVER A]
Whoa! Hey! What's happening?

01:37:45.379 --> 01:37:47.647 position:19% line:83% align:start
[MALE DRIVER B] Move!
We need to get outta here!

01:37:50.250 --> 01:37:51.785 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Run!

01:37:53.086 --> 01:37:54.187 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE screams]

01:37:54.220 --> 01:37:55.789 position:35% line:83% align:start
--[grunts]
--Kaede!

01:37:58.358 --> 01:37:59.893 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE groans]

01:38:07.367 --> 01:38:11.003 position:13% line:89% align:start
[CROWD gasping, murmuring]

01:38:11.036 --> 01:38:16.642 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

01:38:16.675 --> 01:38:19.244 position:21% line:83% align:start
