Let's go!

01:38:23.248 --> 01:38:24.917 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
Where are we going?

01:38:59.450 --> 01:39:02.853 position:16% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] How can I fight
whatever it is he's become?

01:39:03.887 --> 01:39:06.823 position:19% line:83% align:start
