and put an end to both of us

01:39:12.429 --> 01:39:14.965 position:24% line:89% align:start
at the same time.

01:39:14.998 --> 01:39:16.266 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's it.

01:39:16.299 --> 01:39:18.801 position:30% line:83% align:start
The only thing
I can think of to do.

01:39:18.834 --> 01:39:19.935 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
It's funny.

01:39:19.969 --> 01:39:24.140 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've been asking myself
the same question over and over.

01:39:24.173 --> 01:39:26.409 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why didn't I just
let go of your hand?

01:39:26.443 --> 01:39:29.446 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why did I keep
running alongside you?

01:39:29.479 --> 01:39:33.282 position:5% line:83% align:start
I mean, I don't think I've ever
been so scared in my life.

01:39:33.315 --> 01:39:36.085 position:30% line:83% align:start
But, you know,
I remembered something.

01:39:36.118 --> 01:39:37.786 position:24% line:83% align:start
The first time we
studied together.

01:39:37.820 --> 01:39:40.022 position:21% line:83% align:start
It was the happiest
I'd been in a while.

01:39:40.055 --> 01:39:43.192 position:7% line:83% align:start
I know that must sound crazy,
but I've never met anyone

01:39:43.225 --> 01:39:45.161 position:21% line:83% align:start
who enjoys learning
as much as you do.

01:39:45.194 --> 01:39:47.896 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's pretty inspiring.

01:39:47.929 --> 01:39:50.932 position:10% line:83% align:start
When I'm with you, I just--
I feel like I can do anything.

01:39:50.965 --> 01:39:52.934 position:10% line:89% align:start
Like I'm suddenly stronger.

01:39:52.967 --> 01:39:56.004 position:7% line:83% align:start
So I want to be there to give
you strength when you need it.

01:39:56.037 --> 01:39:59.707 position:7% line:83% align:start
If you're fighting something,
then I'm fighting it, too.

01:39:59.741 --> 01:40:01.142 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't forget, okay?

01:40:01.176 --> 01:40:02.310 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're not alone.

01:40:02.343 --> 01:40:04.112 position:24% line:83% align:start
It doesn't matter
how scared I am.

01:40:04.145 --> 01:40:05.980 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm not letting go of your hand.

01:40:06.014 --> 01:40:07.415 position:33% line:89% align:start
Kaede, I...

01:40:08.516 --> 01:40:10.784 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TRAIN ANNOUNCEMER] May I
have your attention, please?

01:40:10.817 --> 01:40:12.353 position:10% line:89% align:start
