01:40:12.387 --> 01:40:14.489 position:27% line:83% align:start
the train cannot
proceed any further.

01:40:14.522 --> 01:40:16.256 position:10% line:89% align:start
This will be our final stop.

01:40:20.794 --> 01:40:21.795 position:27% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS gasping]

01:40:21.828 --> 01:40:23.297 position:21% line:83% align:start
[BEAST ELDER MAN A]
Why is the ground shaking?

01:40:23.330 --> 01:40:25.032 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN W]
It's Ichirohiko's doing.

01:40:25.065 --> 01:40:27.201 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's wreaking havoc
in the human world.

01:40:27.234 --> 01:40:28.368 position:21% line:83% align:start
[BEAST ELDER MAN B]
What occurs in their world

01:40:28.402 --> 01:40:29.937 position:19% line:89% align:start
may resonate in ours,

01:40:29.970 --> 01:40:32.805 position:13% line:83% align:start
but I've never known it to
happen to such an extent.

01:40:32.838 --> 01:40:34.774 position:24% line:83% align:start
This is a conflict
between two humans

01:40:34.807 --> 01:40:37.277 position:19% line:83% align:start
and yet it seems we're
being dragged into it.

01:40:37.311 --> 01:40:38.878 position:21% line:83% align:start
[BEAST ELDER MAN C]
This is exactly why humans

01:40:38.911 --> 01:40:41.314 position:19% line:83% align:start
shouldn't be accepted
into our world!

01:40:42.482 --> 01:40:43.483 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST ELDERS]
Hm?

01:40:43.517 --> 01:40:44.483 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Huh?

01:40:44.518 --> 01:40:48.521 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU grunts]

01:40:48.554 --> 01:40:50.122 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TATARA whimpers]
Lay down!

01:40:50.156 --> 01:40:52.124 position:21% line:83% align:start
