01:40:57.896 --> 01:40:59.232 position:16% line:89% align:start
I need to be out there.

01:40:59.265 --> 01:41:01.166 position:33% line:89% align:start
Helping him.

01:41:01.200 --> 01:41:02.468 position:35% line:89% align:start
Kumatetsu.

