And what exactly do
you think you can do?!

01:41:05.103 --> 01:41:05.971 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Actually...

01:41:06.004 --> 01:41:08.373 position:24% line:83% align:start
..the lord has to
do something first.

01:41:08.406 --> 01:41:10.508 position:5% line:89% align:start
He knows what I'm talking about.

01:41:10.542 --> 01:41:13.245 position:24% line:83% align:start
Maybe he wants to
explain it to everybody.

01:41:13.278 --> 01:41:14.312 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's he suggesting?

01:41:14.346 --> 01:41:17.315 position:24% line:83% align:start
What do you expect
the lord to do?

01:41:17.349 --> 01:41:18.550 position:24% line:89% align:start
Kyuta is stubborn.

01:41:18.583 --> 01:41:21.052 position:21% line:83% align:start
He thinks he can do
everything on his own.

01:41:21.086 --> 01:41:24.155 position:13% line:83% align:start
But he's wrong about that.
He will need help.

01:41:24.189 --> 01:41:26.190 position:13% line:89% align:start
I know I'm not worth much.

01:41:26.224 --> 01:41:28.058 position:24% line:83% align:start
But even a foolish
master like me

01:41:28.092 --> 01:41:30.227 position:7% line:89% align:start
can still help his apprentice.

01:41:30.261 --> 01:41:32.997 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm going fill his soul with
whatever strength he needs

01:41:33.030 --> 01:41:34.999 position:21% line:89% align:start
to win this battle.

01:41:35.032 --> 01:41:37.101 position:27% line:83% align:start
I may be a fool
and a bum and a slob,

01:41:37.134 --> 01:41:39.570 position:10% line:89% align:start
but for him I can be strong!

01:41:39.603 --> 01:41:42.439 position:19% line:83% align:start
--[distant explosion]
--[BEASTS screaming]

01:41:43.941 --> 01:41:45.242 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Hm...

01:41:45.276 --> 01:41:47.944 position:27% line:83% align:start
You have changed
a great deal, Kumatetsu.

01:41:47.977 --> 01:41:50.180 position:24% line:89% align:start
A very great deal.

01:41:50.214 --> 01:41:52.483 position:27% line:83% align:start
You see, what he
is asking me to do

01:41:52.516 --> 01:41:55.285 position:16% line:83% align:start
is to give him the right
to reincarnate.

01:41:55.318 --> 01:41:57.521 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're joking.
He's asking to become a god?

01:41:57.554 --> 01:41:58.555 position:38% line:89% align:start
Absurd.

01:41:58.589 --> 01:42:00.823 position:21% line:83% align:start
That isn't something
granted to just any Beast.

01:42:00.857 --> 01:42:04.027 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yes! Only the lord is given
the chance to reincarnate.

01:42:04.060 --> 01:42:06.329 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

01:42:06.362 --> 01:42:07.463 position:35% line:89% align:start
And now...

01:42:07.497 --> 01:42:10.033 position:13% line:89% align:start
...Kumatetsu is the lord.

01:42:10.066 --> 01:42:11.900 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LORD]
Think carefully, Kumatetsu.

01:42:11.933 --> 01:42:16.306 position:10% line:83% align:start
Once you decide to do this,
there can be no turning back.

01:42:16.339 --> 01:42:18.408 position:13% line:89% align:start
So tell me, are you sure?

01:42:23.245 --> 01:42:25.080 position:5% line:89% align:start
It is as I thought it would be.

01:42:25.113 --> 01:42:26.181 position:19% line:89% align:start
Looking at your eyes,

01:42:26.214 --> 01:42:29.117 position:10% line:83% align:start
I can tell there is no trace
of doubt in your heart.

01:42:40.295 --> 01:42:42.296 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA gasps]

01:42:42.331 --> 01:42:44.965 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
There he is.

01:42:44.999 --> 01:42:45.567 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where'd he go?

01:42:45.600 --> 01:42:47.134 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE gasps]

01:42:53.674 --> 01:42:55.209 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE, KYUTA gasp]

01:43:01.349 --> 01:43:02.882 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hurry!

01:43:13.226 --> 01:43:14.260 position:24% line:89% align:start
You should go now.

01:43:14.294 --> 01:43:16.596 position:5% line:89% align:start
He won't notice. He's after me.

01:43:17.964 --> 01:43:19.399 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kaede!

01:43:19.432 --> 01:43:21.067 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KAEDE]
What do want, huh?!

01:43:21.101 --> 01:43:23.370 position:16% line:83% align:start
To hunt down your enemy
and rip him apart?

01:43:23.403 --> 01:43:24.637 position:27% line:89% align:start
To destroy him?

01:43:24.671 --> 01:43:27.940 position:16% line:83% align:start
Do you really think that
will make you happy?

01:43:27.973 --> 01:43:30.242 position:24% line:83% align:start
You may look like
some giant monster,

01:43:30.276 --> 01:43:33.312 position:16% line:83% align:start
but you're just a human
after petty vengeance!

01:43:33.345 --> 01:43:36.482 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't you get it?
We all carry darkness inside us!

01:43:36.515 --> 01:43:38.183 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ren does, and so do I!

01:43:38.217 --> 01:43:39.585 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's not just you.

01:43:39.618 --> 01:43:41.453 position:19% line:89% align:start
But we can fight back.

01:43:41.487 --> 01:43:45.190 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm fighting it right now,
and believe me, it isn't easy.

01:43:45.224 --> 01:43:47.126 position:16% line:89% align:start
But you didn't even try.

01:43:47.159 --> 01:43:49.194 position:5% line:89% align:start
You just let it swallow you up.

01:43:49.228 --> 01:43:52.598 position:30% line:83% align:start
And that makes
you weaker than us.

01:43:52.631 --> 01:43:55.166 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're not going to win,
do you hear me?!

01:43:55.199 --> 01:43:58.302 position:27% line:89% align:start
[WHALE bellows]

01:43:58.336 --> 01:43:59.605 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on!

01:44:01.707 --> 01:44:07.412 position:16% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA, KAEDE grunting]

01:44:07.445 --> 01:44:08.613 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wait, come back!

01:44:08.646 --> 01:44:10.114 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
I have no choice.

01:44:10.148 --> 01:44:13.384 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ichirohiko! Look!

01:44:17.154 --> 01:44:21.158 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm going to take the Darkness
from you into myself!

01:44:26.430 --> 01:44:29.166 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CHICO squeaks]

01:44:29.199 --> 01:44:32.169 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeals]

01:44:35.172 --> 01:44:38.040 position:33% line:89% align:start
Ren, no. No!

01:44:40.610 --> 01:44:42.446 position:13% line:89% align:start
You and I are leaving now.

01:44:42.479 --> 01:44:44.146 position:7% line:89% align:start
We're not fit for this world.

01:44:44.180 --> 01:44:45.314 position:33% line:89% align:start
No! Stop it!

01:44:45.348 --> 01:44:48.485 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA yells]

01:44:48.518 --> 01:44:50.052 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't let it take you!

01:44:50.085 --> 01:44:53.690 position:21% line:89% align:start
[yelling continues]

01:44:53.723 --> 01:44:56.125 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[TATARA] Kyuta!
--[KYUTA gasps]

01:44:59.462 --> 01:45:03.232 position:30% line:89% align:start
[WHALE moans]

01:45:09.572 --> 01:45:10.673 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA]
What in the--?

01:45:10.706 --> 01:45:13.709 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
Kyuta! The sword is Kumatetsu!

01:45:13.742 --> 01:45:15.410 position:30% line:83% align:start
He thought you
might need some help,

01:45:15.443 --> 01:45:18.513 position:24% line:83% align:start
so he reincarnated
into that sword.

01:45:18.546 --> 01:45:22.217 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is that really... you?

01:45:22.250 --> 01:45:23.785 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TATARA]
He chose what to become.

01:45:23.818 --> 01:45:26.588 position:21% line:83% align:start
He said he would be
the sword in your soul.

01:45:26.621 --> 01:45:29.657 position:10% line:89% align:start
The sword in my... my soul.

01:45:29.691 --> 01:45:32.427 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
You have one, don't you?

01:45:32.460 --> 01:45:34.362 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] What?
You don't make any sense.

01:45:34.395 --> 01:45:37.331 position:16% line:83% align:start
How much clearer do you
need me to make it for you?

01:45:37.364 --> 01:45:40.234 position:24% line:83% align:start
You grab the sword
that's in your soul.

01:45:40.267 --> 01:45:43.237 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA whimpers]

01:45:49.343 --> 01:45:52.079 position:24% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU laughs]
Not bad for a human kid!

01:45:52.112 --> 01:45:53.780 position:7% line:89% align:start
I knew I was right about you.

01:45:55.616 --> 01:45:59.720 position:7% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU] Well, now you're a
nine-year-old named Kyuta.

01:46:02.154 --> 01:46:03.489 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now we're in business!

01:46:03.523 --> 01:46:06.626 position:16% line:83% align:start
I hope you are ready for
some serious training!

01:46:06.659 --> 01:46:13.165 position:24% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU laughs]

01:46:13.199 --> 01:46:19.272 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA whimpers]

01:46:24.477 --> 01:46:25.778 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Kyuta!

01:46:25.811 --> 01:46:28.213 position:5% line:89% align:start
What are you doing? Stop crying!

01:46:28.246 --> 01:46:29.080 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:46:29.114 --> 01:46:31.616 position:24% line:83% align:start
You know how much
I hate crybabies.

01:46:36.821 --> 01:46:39.357 position:16% line:89% align:start
Shut up! I'm not crying!

01:46:45.597 --> 01:46:46.364 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

01:46:46.398 --> 01:46:47.732 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO grunts]

01:46:53.838 --> 01:46:55.406 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Now, get ready.

01:46:57.474 --> 01:46:59.543 position:33% line:83% align:start
--Okay, kid.
--Careful.

01:47:03.847 --> 01:47:04.848 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Not yet.

01:47:04.882 --> 01:47:07.351 position:27% line:83% align:start
Keep your senses
sharp and watch.

01:47:12.523 --> 01:47:13.857 position:41% line:89% align:start
There!

01:47:23.232 --> 01:47:27.270 position:5% line:83% align:start
[KYUTA] He appears in human form
just before the whale leaps out.

01:47:27.303 --> 01:47:28.638 position:38% line:89% align:start
Gotcha!

01:47:30.640 --> 01:47:32.342 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Focus on a single point.

01:47:32.375 --> 01:47:34.844 position:27% line:83% align:start
Strike there and
do not hesitate.

01:47:46.455 --> 01:47:47.756 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Now! Go!

01:47:47.789 --> 01:47:50.492 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA grunts]

01:47:50.525 --> 01:47:58.199 position:13% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA, KUMATETSU yelling]

01:48:03.572 --> 01:48:06.642 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO rasps]

01:48:12.446 --> 01:48:19.587 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO screams]

01:48:19.620 --> 01:48:22.790 position:30% line:89% align:start
[WHALE moans]

01:48:34.969 --> 01:48:37.370 position:24% line:89% align:start
He did it. Right?

01:48:37.404 --> 01:48:38.939 position:44% line:89% align:start
No.

01:48:38.973 --> 01:48:40.507 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:48:42.275 --> 01:48:44.611 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO]
You stupid human...

01:48:44.644 --> 01:48:48.581 position:30% line:89% align:start
I hate you...

01:48:48.615 --> 01:48:52.786 position:33% line:83% align:start
Ichirohiko.
You and I are the same.

01:48:56.622 --> 01:49:00.626 position:13% line:83% align:start
We were raised by Beasts,
but born with human hearts.

01:49:19.044 --> 01:49:21.212 position:19% line:89% align:start
This isn't my bedroom.

01:49:22.613 --> 01:49:23.982 position:33% line:89% align:start
Where am I?

01:49:25.383 --> 01:49:26.784 position:27% line:89% align:start
Father, Mother?

01:49:26.818 --> 01:49:29.854 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're here, too? And Jiromaru?

01:49:29.887 --> 01:49:33.357 position:24% line:83% align:start
I don't understand
what's going on here.

01:49:33.391 --> 01:49:37.028 position:13% line:83% align:start
I remember us all going to
the stadium together, but then.

01:49:37.061 --> 01:49:39.664 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ICHIROHIKO groans]

01:49:44.902 --> 01:49:46.436 position:27% line:89% align:start
I've seen this.

01:49:46.470 --> 01:49:48.806 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's Kyuta's.

01:50:03.453 --> 01:50:05.021 position:33% line:83% align:start
[KUMATETSU]
Snap out of it.

01:50:05.055 --> 01:50:07.591 position:21% line:83% align:start
When I decide to do
something, it gets done.

01:50:07.624 --> 01:50:09.291 position:21% line:89% align:start
One way or another.

01:50:09.325 --> 01:50:10.392 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA sighs]

01:50:10.426 --> 01:50:11.795 position:24% line:89% align:start
Trust me, I know.

01:50:11.828 --> 01:50:13.462 position:10% line:89% align:start
Then quit brooding, already,

01:50:13.496 --> 01:50:15.065 position:19% line:83% align:start
or I'll kick your butt
from the inside.

01:50:15.098 --> 01:50:17.566 position:13% line:89% align:start
Shut up. I'm not brooding.

01:50:17.600 --> 01:50:18.901 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now that's more like it!

01:50:18.934 --> 01:50:20.770 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

01:50:20.803 --> 01:50:22.538 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll do whatever I want.

01:50:22.571 --> 01:50:23.906 position:24% line:89% align:start
You just watch me.

01:50:23.939 --> 01:50:28.077 position:27% line:83% align:start
Oh! You can bet
I'll be watching you.

01:50:28.110 --> 01:50:31.514 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA chuckles]

01:50:31.547 --> 01:50:35.650 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KUMATETSU chuckles]

01:50:51.933 --> 01:50:54.368 position:5% line:83% align:start
[MALE NEWS REPORTER] An enormous
explosion occurred last night

01:50:54.401 --> 01:50:57.639 position:5% line:83% align:start
in Shibuya, caused by the crash
of an unmanned runaway truck.

01:50:57.672 --> 01:50:59.908 position:16% line:83% align:start
Many people were injured
as they fled the scene,

01:50:59.941 --> 01:51:02.643 position:7% line:83% align:start
however, none of the injuries
were reported as critical.

01:51:02.676 --> 01:51:05.013 position:16% line:83% align:start
Police received numerous
perplexing reports

01:51:05.046 --> 01:51:07.115 position:19% line:83% align:start
of a mysterious shadow
that appeared to be

01:51:07.148 --> 01:51:08.582 position:21% line:89% align:start
shaped like a whale.

01:51:08.615 --> 01:51:10.517 position:19% line:83% align:start
Nothing matching this
description was caught

01:51:10.551 --> 01:51:12.886 position:21% line:83% align:start
on any of the area's
security cameras.

01:51:14.955 --> 01:51:20.594 position:24% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheering]

01:51:20.627 --> 01:51:21.962 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
Impressive, huh?

01:51:21.995 --> 01:51:23.730 position:5% line:89% align:start
But he wasn't always like this.

01:51:23.764 --> 01:51:25.799 position:30% line:83% align:start
Even our Kyuta
started out as a weakling.

01:51:25.833 --> 01:51:27.533 position:7% line:89% align:start
In other words, there is hope.

01:51:27.567 --> 01:51:30.436 position:10% line:83% align:start
If you mind your master and
train very hard every day,

01:51:30.469 --> 01:51:32.772 position:16% line:83% align:start
you runts might actually
become strong, too.

01:51:32.805 --> 01:51:34.373 position:19% line:89% align:start
[TRAINEE BEASTS gasp]

01:51:34.407 --> 01:51:36.375 position:19% line:89% align:start
There may be a chance.

01:51:36.409 --> 01:51:37.910 position:21% line:89% align:start
A very slim chance.

01:51:37.944 --> 01:51:39.512 position:19% line:89% align:start
[TRAINEE BEASTS sigh]

01:51:39.545 --> 01:51:41.948 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why did I spend so many
years dithering?

01:51:41.981 --> 01:51:44.482 position:13% line:83% align:start
I should have reincarnated
when I had the chance!

01:51:44.517 --> 01:51:47.787 position:7% line:83% align:start
I could be a god right now if
I'd just made up my mind sooner.

01:51:47.820 --> 01:51:49.755 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is no time for regrets.

01:51:49.789 --> 01:51:51.523 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's a day of celebration.

01:51:51.556 --> 01:51:53.825 position:24% line:89% align:start
Cheers! To Kyuta!

01:51:53.859 --> 01:51:56.394 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ah! And look over there.

01:51:56.428 --> 01:51:57.495 position:16% line:89% align:start
From what I understand,

01:51:57.529 --> 01:52:01.900 position:5% line:83% align:start
that young lady was instrumental
in Kyuta's success.

01:52:01.933 --> 01:52:04.603 position:5% line:89% align:start
Kaede! What are you doing here?

01:52:04.636 --> 01:52:05.604 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KAEDE laughs]

01:52:05.637 --> 01:52:07.672 position:19% line:89% align:start
I was invited, silly.

01:52:07.706 --> 01:52:09.841 position:19% line:83% align:start
And here, I dropped it
that night,

01:52:09.875 --> 01:52:11.910 position:19% line:83% align:start
and it wasn't exactly
easy to find again.

01:52:11.943 --> 01:52:14.678 position:7% line:89% align:start
I thought you'd like it back.

01:52:14.712 --> 01:52:15.847 position:27% line:89% align:start
I would. Thanks.

01:52:15.881 --> 01:52:18.582 position:24% line:83% align:start
And an application
for the entrance exams.

01:52:18.616 --> 01:52:19.683 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you say?

01:52:19.717 --> 01:52:22.019 position:24% line:83% align:start
Do you still wanna
give it a try?

01:52:22.053 --> 01:52:23.654 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KYUTA sighs]

01:52:23.687 --> 01:52:26.824 position:16% line:83% align:start
I know a lot's happened,
but I thought, maybe...

01:52:28.158 --> 01:52:29.693 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'll do it.

01:52:29.727 --> 01:52:31.996 position:38% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
Yay! Heh!

01:52:32.029 --> 01:52:35.799 position:5% line:83% align:start
I knew you were gonna say that!
We'll study together, 'kay?

01:52:35.833 --> 01:52:38.534 position:30% line:83% align:start
[BEAST MAN X]
The fireworks are starting!

01:52:43.140 --> 01:52:53.149 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BEASTS cheer]

01:53:09.665 --> 01:53:10.999 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

01:53:13.936 --> 01:53:15.737 position:33% line:89% align:start
[BOTH laugh]

01:53:15.771 --> 01:53:17.906 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
After that, Kyuta left Jutengai

01:53:17.940 --> 01:53:19.608 position:10% line:89% align:start
and the world of the Beasts.

01:53:19.641 --> 01:53:21.476 position:10% line:89% align:start
He never held a sword again.

01:53:21.510 --> 01:53:24.246 position:16% line:83% align:start
[TATARA] Even so, there
is no stronger swordsman.

01:53:24.279 --> 01:53:25.414 position:33% line:83% align:start
[HYAKUSHUBO]
That's right.

01:53:25.446 --> 01:53:28.951 position:10% line:83% align:start
Because in his soul there is
